I-AMs yaseWelsh ixhalabile 'ngokubukeka njengeemapets'
Kukho ukuphazamiseka phakathi kwee-AMs kwisindululo sokuba isihloko sazo kufuneka sitshintshwe sibe yi-MWPs (iLungu lePalamente yaseWales).
Kuye kwavela ngenxa yezicwangciso zokutshintsha igama leendibano kwiPalamente yaseWales.
Abaphathi bezopolitiko kwiinkalo ezahlukahlukeneyo bakhathazekile kukuba oku kunokubangela ukuba bahlekiswe.
Omnye uMbutho wezaBasebenzi wathi iqela lakhe lalikhathazekile "kuyahambelana neTwp nePwp".
Kubafundi abangekho eWales: NgesiWelsh i-twp ithetha i-daft kwaye i-pwp ithetha i-poo.
Iqela lePlaid AM lithi lonke eli qela "alivuyiswa" yaye liye lacebisa ngeendlela ezahlukileyo.
UmGcini weNgqesho waseWelsh uthe iqela lakhe "linengqondo evulekileyo" malunga nokutshintsha kwegama, kodwa waphawula ukuba yayikukutsiba okufutshane okuvela kwi-MWP ukuya kwi-Muppet.
Kule meko, ileta w yesiWelsh ibizwa ngendlela efanayo neeleta u yesiNgesi saseYorkshire.
IKomishoni yeNdlu, ngoku elungiselela umthetho wokutshintshwa kwegama, yathi: "Isigqibo sokugqibela sokuthi amalungu endlu abizwa njani siya kuba ngumcimbi wamalungu ngokwawo".
UMthetho kaRhulumente waseWales ka-2017 wanika iNdlu yoWiso-mthetho igunya lokutshintsha igama layo.
NgoJuni, iKhomishini yapapasha iziphumo zokudibana noluntu ngeziphakamiso ezifumene inkxaso ebanzi yokubiza intlanganiso iPalamente yaseWales.
Kwimiba ye-AMs' title, iKhomishini yancoma amalungu ePalamente yaseWales okanye iiWMPs, kodwa ukhetho lwe-MWP lufumene inkxaso enkulu ekubonisaneni noluntu.
I-AMs ngokucacileyo icebisa ezinye iindlela, kodwa umzabalazo wokufikelela kwisivumelwano unokuba yintloko ye-Presiding Officer, uElin Jones, okulindeleke ukuba angenise umthetho weenguqu kwiiveki ezimbalwa.
Umthetho wenguqu uza kuquka ezinye iinguqu kwindlela indibano esebenza ngayo, kuquka nemithetho engokungafaneleki kwee-AM kunye nokuqulunqwa kwenkqubo yekomiti.
I-AMs iya kuba nelizwi lokugqibela kumbuzo wokuba kufuneka babizwe njani xa bexoxa ngomthetho.
Abantu baseMacedonia baya kuvota kwi-referendum yokutshintsha igama lelizwe
Abavoti baza kuvota ngeCawa ukuba bangatshintsha igama lelizwe labo libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia".
Olu khetho lwabantu lwalwenzelwe ukuzama ukusombulula imbambano yeminyaka emininzi nelizwe elingummelwane iGrisi, elinephondo lalo elibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.
IAthene kudala igxininisa kwelokuba igama lommelwane wayo wasemntla limela ibango kummandla wayo yaye izihlandlo ezininzi iye yachas' amalungelo ayo angamalungu e-EU ne-NATO.
UMongameli waseMakedoni uGjorge Ivanov, ongakholelwayo ukuba kwenziwe uvavanyo-zimvo lokutshintsha igama, uthe akayi kuyihoxisa loo nto.
Noko ke, abaxhasi bale ntetho, kuquka iNkulumbuso uZoran Zaev, bathi ukutshintsha kwegama lixabiso nje elifuneka lihlawulwe ukuze lijoyine i-EU neNATO.
Iintsimbi Zengqungquthela YaseSt. Martin Zithi Cwaka Njengoko Iicawa Zilwa EHarlem
"Ngokwembali, abantu abadala endathetha nabo bathi kwakukho ibhari necawa kuzo zonke iimbombo", watsho uMnu. Adams.
"Namhlanje, akukho nanye kwezi".
Wathi ukulahleka kweebhari kwakusengqiqweni.
Wathi, "Abantu badibana ngendlela eyahlukileyo" kule mihla.
"Iindawo zokutyela azisekho njengamagumbi abantu abahlala kuwo apho abantu baya rhoqo".
Ngokuphathelele iicawa, uxhalabele ukuba imali evela ekuthengisweni kwezinto ezikhoyo ayiyi kuhlala ixesha elide njengoko iinkokeli zilindele ukuba kube njalo, "kwaye kungekudala okanye kamva ziya kubuyela apho zazisuka khona".
Wongezelela esithi, iicawa zinokuthatyathelwa indawo zizakhiwo ezinamagumbi ahlala abantu abangayi kunceda iindawo ezingcwele eziseleyo zommandla.
Wathi: "Uninzi lwabantu abathenga izindlu kwezi zakhiwo luya kuba ngabantu abamhlophe, yaye ngenxa yoko luya kukhawulezisa ukuvalwa kwazo zonke ezi cawa kuba akulindelekanga ukuba uninzi lwabantu abaza kuhlala kwezi zindlu lube ngamalungu ezi cawa".
Zombini ezi cawa zakhiwa ngamabandla amhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe sisixeko esikhulu sabantsundu - iMetropolitan Community ngowe-1870, neSt. Martin's kwishumi leminyaka kamva.
Ibandla lokuqala leMethodist elimhlophe lafuduka ngeminyaka yo1930.
Ibandla labantu abantsundu elalikhonza kufutshane nalo lathatha isakhiwo salo.
ISt. Martin's yathwalwa libandla labamnyama phantsi koMfundisi uJohn Howard Johnson, owakhokela ukuvalwa kweevenkile ezise-125th Street, eyona ndlela iphambili yokuthenga eHarlem, ezazikhanyela ukuqesha okanye ukukhuthaza abantu abantsundu.
Umlilo ngowe-1939 washiya isakhiwo sonakaliswe kakhulu, kodwa njengoko amarhamente kaPeter Johnson ayesenza izicwangciso zokwakha kwakhona, ayenza yasebenza icarillon.
Umfundisi uDavid Johnson, unyana kaPatriar Johnson nomlandeli wakhe eSt. Martin, ngokuzingca wabiza ikharillon ngokuthi "iintsimbi zabantu abahluphekayo".
Ingcali eyayidlala le carillon ngoJulayi yathi le yayiyenye into: "Yingqokelela yenkcubeko" yaye "sisixhobo esingenakuthelekiswa nanto esingokwembali".
Ingcali, uTiffany Ng weYunivesithi yaseMichigan, nayo yaphawula ukuba yayiyimbovane yokuqala ehlabathini eyayidlalwa ngumculi omnyama, uDionisio A. Lind, owafudukela kwimbovane enkulu kwiCawa yaseRiverside kwiminyaka eli-18 eyadlulayo.
UMr. Merriweather uthe iSt. Martin ayizange imthathel' indawo.
Oko kuye kwenzeka kwiSt. Martin kwiinyanga ezimbalwa ezidluleyo kuye kwaba libali elinzima lezakhiwo neekontraka, ezinye eziye zaqeshwa ziinkokeli zecawa, ezinye ziqeshwa yicawa yamaBhishobhi.
Iqumrhu elilawulayo - iqumrhu elilawulayo lecawa, eliqulethwe ziinkokeli ezingabantu - labhalela ubhishophu ngoJulayi kuba lalinenkxalabo yokuba ubhishophu "wayeza kuzama ukudlulisela iindleko" kwiqumrhu elilawulayo, nangona ubhishophu ebengekho ekuqeshweni kwezakhiwo nabenzi bakontraka ababethunyelwe liqumrhu.
Abanye abantu baseparishi bakhalazela ukungabikho kokungafihlisi kwecawa.
UShark wenzakalisa umntwana oneminyaka eli-13 ubudala xa wayese-lobster diving eCalifornia
Amagosa athi, ngoMgqibelo inyamakazi yahlasela yaza yonzakalisa inkwenkwe eneminyaka eli-13 ubudala ngoxa yayitsiba ifuna i-lobster eCalifornia ngosuku lokuqala lwexesha le-lobster.
Olu hlaselo lwenzeka ngaphambi nje kweye-7 kusasa kufuphi neBeacon's Beach e-Encinitas.
UChad Hammel uxelele i-KSWB-TV eSan Diego ukuba ebesehlela emanzini nabahlobo bakhe kangange siqingatha seyure ngentsasa yangoMgqibelo xa weva inkwenkwe ikhala icela uncedo waza wadlula neqela ukuze liyincede iphume emanzini.
UHammel wathi ekuqaleni wayecinga ukuba kukuchulumanca nje kokubambisa i-lobster, kodwa emva koko "waqonda ukuba wayemkhwaza, 'Ndimilisiwe!
Ndibethwe!'
"I-clavicle yakhe yayikrazukile", uHammel wathi wayiphawula xa efika kule nkwenkwe.
"Ndakhwaza ndathi kubo bonke: 'Kukho ukrebe emanzini!'" wongezelela uHammel.
Le nkwenkwe yathunyelwa ngenqwelo-moya kwiSibhedlele Sabantwana iRady eSan Diego apho ibhalwe khona kwimeko enzima.
Azinikelwa iinkcukacha ngohlobo lo shark olwahlaselayo.
Umphathi weLifeguard uLarry Giles uthe kwingxoxo neendaba ukuba shark ibonwe kule ndawo kwiiveki ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo, kodwa kwafunyaniswa ukuba ayilohlobo oluyingozi lomnenga.
UGiles wongezelela ngelithi ixhoba lafumana amanxeba entloko kumphezulu womzimba walo.
Amagosa avale indlela eya elunxwemeni esuka ePonto Beach eCasablad ukuya eSwami's e-Ecinitas kangangeeyure ezingama-48 ngenxa yophando kunye neenjongo zokhuseleko.
UGiles waphawula ukuba kukho iintlobo zeentaka ezingaphezu kwe-135 kuloo mmandla, kodwa inkoliso yazo ayigqalwa njengeyingozi.
Izicwangciso zeSainsbury zokungena kwiimarike zobuhle zase-UK
ISainsbury's ithatha indawo yeBoots, Superdrug neDebenhams ngezitolo ezinkulu ezinemigca yobuhle ezenziwe ngabasebenzi abangabancedisi abaziingcali.
Njengengxenye yokunyusa ukuthengisa izinto zokuthambisa kwi-UK ezixabisa i-£2.8 billion, eziqhubeka zikhula ngoxa ukuthengisa izinto zefashoni nezokusetyenziswa ekhaya kuncipha, ezi ndlela zokuthambisa ezinkulu ziza kuvavanywa kwiivenkile ezili-11 kulo lonke eli lizwe zize zihanjiswe kwiivenkile ezininzi kunyaka ozayo ukuba ziyaphumelela.
Olu tyalo-mali kubuhle luza njengoko iivenkile ezinkulu zifuna iindlela zokusebenzisa indawo eselugcinweni eyayikade isetyenziselwa iTV, ii-microwave nezinto zasekhaya.
Ivenkile iSainsbury's ithi iza kuphinda kabini ubungakanani bemveliso yayo yobuhle ize ifikelele kwiimveliso ezingama-3 000, kuquka iimveliso ezinjengeRevlon, Essie, Tweezerman noGqirha PawPaw okwesihlandlo sokuqala.
Iintlobo ezikhoyo zeL'Oreal, iMaybelline neBurt's Bees nazo ziza kufumana indawo engakumbi eneendawo ezibhalwe ngegama elifana nezo zifumaneka kwiivenkile ezinjengeBoots.
Ivenkile enkulu ikwakhupha kwakhona uluhlu lwezinto zokuthambisa iBoutique ukuze uninzi lweemveliso zilungele iivegan - into efunwa kakhulu ngabathengi abaselula.
Ukongeza, umthengisi weziqholo iFragrance Shop izakuvavanya izibonelelo kwiivenkile ezimbini zeSainsbury, eyokuqala kuzo yavula eCroydon, kumazantsi eLondon, kwiveki ephelileyo ngelixa eyesibini ivula eSelly Oak, eBirmingham, kamva kulo nyaka.
Ukuthenga nge-Internet nokutshintshela ekuthengeni ukutya okuncinane imihla ngemihla kwiivenkile zokutya zasekuhlaleni kuthetha ukuba iivenkile ezinkulu kufuneka zenze okungakumbi ukuze ziqwebele abantu ukuba beze.
UMike Coupe, oyintloko yequmrhu elilawulayo leSainsbury's, uthe ezi venkile ziza kufana nevenkile ezinkulu njengoko eli jelo levenkile ezinkulu lizama ukuzilwela kwiivenkile ezenza izinto ezisezantsi iAldi neLidl ngeenkonzo ezingakumbi nezinto ezingekho mgangathweni.
ISainsbury's ibeka iivenkile zeArgos kwiivenkile ezininzi yaye iye yazisa neeHabitat ezininzi ukususela oko yathenga le mizi yogcino-mveliso kwiminyaka emibini edluleyo, nto leyo ethi iye yakhuthaza ukuthengiswa kwevenkile zokutya yaza yenza ukuba ezi zinto zithengiweyo zibe nenzuzo engakumbi.
Iinzame zangaphambili zevenkile enkulu zokulungisa amacandelo ayo okwenza ubuhle namayeza zaphelela emoyeni.
USainsbury wazama intsebenziswano neBoots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yama-2000, kodwa ukudibana kwaphela emva kwengxabano malunga nendlela yokwahlula ingeniso evela kwiivenkile zesebe kwiivenkile ezinkulu.
Eli qhinga litsha liza emva kokuba iSainsbury ithengise ishishini layo lamavenkile angama-281 kwiCelesio, umnini we-Lloyds Pharmacy chain, nge-£125m, kwiminyaka emithathu eyadlulayo.
Yathi iLloyds iza kudlala indima kwisicwangciso, ngokongeza uluhlu olubanzi lweempawu zokhathalelo lolusu kubandakanya iLa Roche-Posay kunye neVichy kwiivenkile ezine.
UPaul Mills-Hicks, umlawuli wezorhwebo eSainsbury, wathi: "Siye satshintsha indlela ezibonakala ngayo iindawo zethu zokuzilungisa ukuze sivulele abathengi bethu ithuba elingakumbi.
Kwakhona siye satyala imali kumaqabane ethu aqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo aza kuba khona ukuze anikele icebiso.
Iintlobo zeempawu zethu zenzelwe ukwanelisa zonke iimfuno yaye imeko-bume enomtsalane neendawo ezifanelekileyo zenza ukuba ngoku sibe yindawo entle ekholisayo eyenza umngeni kwindlela endala yokuthenga".
UPeter Jones 'ugqajukelwe' nguHolly Willoughby emva kokuba eshiye isivumelwano see-£11million
Inkwenkwezi yeDragons Den uPeter Jones 'ngomsindo' emva kokuba umbonisi weTV uHolly Willoughby ekhuphe i-£11million kwisivumelwano sakhe noshishino lweempawu zokuphila ukuze agxile kwizivumelwano zakhe ezintsha neMarks and Spencer ne-ITV
UWilloughby akanalo ixesha lokuthengisa iimpahla zakhe zasekhaya kunye nezinto zokuthambisa.
Ishishini labo lalisele lifaniswa neGoop kaGwyneth Paltrow.
Lo mninimzi we-This Morning, oneminyaka engama-37 ubudala, uye kwi-Instagram ukuze avakalise ukuba uyemka.
UHolly Willoughby ushiye inkwenkwezi yeDragons' Den uPeter Jones ecaphukile ngokurhoxa kwishishini labo elinengeniso elenza ubomi bube bhetele ngomzuzu wokugqibela - ukuze ajolise kwizivumelwano zakhe ezintsha ze-bumper kunye neMarks & Spencer kunye ne-ITV.
Iindaba zithi uJones "wacaphuka" xa intombazana yeTV evuma ngethuba lentlanganiso ebandayo ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu le-impire yakhe yezoshishino eMarlow, Buckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano zakhe ezintsha - ezixabisa ukuya kwi-£1.5 yezigidi - zithetha ukuba akasenawo ixesha elaneleyo lokuzinikela kwiimpahla zasekhaya kunye nezixhobo zeempahla zabo ezibizwa ngokuba yiTruly.
Eli shishini lalinganiswa neGwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand kwaye lalingqongwe ukuba liphindwe kabini ubutyebi beWilloughby obuqikelelwa kwizigidi ezili-11 zeephawundi.
Njengoko uWilloughby, oneminyaka engama-37 ubudala, wathatha i-Instagram ukubhengeza ukuba uyemka eTruly, uJones wasuka eBritani waya kwenye yeendawo zakhe zokuhlala.
Omnye umthombo wathi: "Ngokwenene yayikokokuqala kwezinto eziphambili zikaHolly.
Yayiza kuba likamva lakhe lexesha elide elaliza kumbona kwiinkulungwane eziliqela ezizayo.
Isigqibo sakhe sokurhoxa samothusa wonke umntu obandakanyekileyo.
Akukho namnye owayenokukukholelwa oko kwakusenzeka ngoLwesibini, kwakusondele kakhulu ekutyhilweni.
Kukho indawo yokugcina impahla epheleleyo kwisikhululo saseMarlow ekulungele ukuthengiswa".
Iingcali zikholelwa ekubeni ukuhamba komntu obonisa le Mvulo, ongomnye weenkwenkwezi zaseBritani ezinemali eninzi, kunokuyibiza imali eninzi inkampani ngenxa yotyalo-mali oluninzi kwimveliso eqala kwizikhuseli neekhandlela ukuya kwiimpahla nezambatho, kunye nokulibaziseka kokukhutshwa kwayo.
Yaye oko kunokuthetha ukuphela kobuhlobo obude.
Umama wabantwana abathathu uWilloughby nomyeni wakhe uDan Baldwin baye basondelelana noJones nomfazi wakhe uTara Capp iminyaka elishumi.
UWilloughby waseka iTruly kunye neCapp ngo-2016 kwaye uJones, 52, wajoyina njengosihlalo ngoMatshi.
Izibini zihlala kunye yaye uJones une-40 ekhulwini kwifemu kaBaldwin yemveliso kamabonwakude.
UWilloughby uza kuba ngunozakuzaku weM&S kwaye uza kungena endaweni kaAnt McPartlin njengomamkeli we-ITV's I'm A Celebrity.
Umthombo osondele kuJones uthe izolo ebusuku "Asizukuphawula ngemicimbi yakhe yeshishini".
'Sathetha ngendlela engqwabalala saza sathandana'
Wenza intlekisa ngezimvo ezigxekayo ezaziza kuvela kumajelo eendaba ngenxa yokwenza intetho abanye ababeza kuyigqala njenge "engengengomongameli" nangenxa yokuba enethemba kakhulu kwinkokeli yaseMntla Korea.
Kutheni le nto uMongameli uTrump eye wancama izinto ezininzi kangaka?
UTrump wathi ngelizwi lakhe elihlekisayo "elibonisa ukuba ungumgcini-ndaba".
"Andizange ndinikezele nantoni na".
Uthe uKim unomdla kwindibano yesibini emva kokuba intlanganiso yabo yokuqala eSingapore ngoJuni yayigunyiswe nguTrump njengenyathelo elikhulu lokuyekisa iNqola yaseMntla Korea.
Kodwa ke, iingxoxo zokupheliswa kwezikhali zenyukliya ziye zavalwa.
Ngaphezu kweenyanga ezintathu emva kwendibano eyayiseSingapore ngoJuni, ummeli omkhulu waseMntla Korea uRi Yong Ho waxelela iinkokeli zehlabathi kwiNtlanganiso yeNtlanganiso yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba uMntla awuboni "impendulo elinganayo" evela e-U.S. kwiintshukumo zokuyekisa ukuzikhupha izixhobo zaseMntla Korea.
Uthe endaweni yoko, i-US iyaqhubeka nokubeka izigwebo ezijoliswe ekuqhubekeni noxinzelelo.
UTump wathetha ngelizwi elinomdla ngakumbi kwintetho yakhe.
Wathi: "Sisebenza kakuhle kakhulu neNorth Korea".
"Sasiza kulwa imfazwe neNorth Korea.
Kwakuza kubulawa izigidi zabantu.
Ngoku sinolwalamano oluhle".
Wathi imigudu yakhe yokuphucula ubudlelwane noKim iye yazisa iziphumo ezintle - ukuphelisa iimvavanyo zothweso, ukunceda ukukhulula amabanjwa nokubuyisela amagumbi amajoni aseMerika ekhaya.
Yaye wayikhusela indlela yakhe engaqhelekanga yokuthetha ngolwalamano lwakhe noKim.
"Kulula ukuba ngumongameli, kodwa endaweni yokuba abantu abali-10 000 bangene kule ndawo izaliswe ngabantu, bekuza kuba nabantu abangama-200 abemi kanye apha", utshilo uTrump, esalatha isihlwele esiphambi kwakhe.
I-Indonesia Iitsunami Nenyikima Zonakalisa Isiqithi, Zibulala Amakhulu
Ngokomzekelo, emva kwenyikima yaseLombok, imibutho engekho phantsi kolawulo lukarhulumente yasemzini yaxelelwa ukuba yayingafuneki.
Nangona abantu baseLombok abangaphezu kwe - 10 ekhulwini babefuduswe, akuzange kubhengezwe intlekele yelizwe, nto leyo eyayifuneka ukuze kuncedwe amazwe ngamazwe.
"Kwiimeko ezininzi, ngelishwa, baye bachaza ngokucacileyo ukuba abaceli uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe, ngoko ke kunzima", uNksk Sumbung utshilo.
Nangona iSave the Children ibeka iqela eliza kuya ePalu, akuqinisekanga ukuba abasebenzi basemzini bangakwazi ukusebenza phaya.
UMnu. Sutopo, osisithethi se-Arhente kaZwelonke Yeentlekele, wathi amagosa aseIndonesia aye ahlola imeko yasePalu ukuze abone enoba amaziko ehlabathi aza kuvunyelwa na ukuba abe negalelo kumgudu wokunikela uncedo.
Ngenxa yokungcangcazela komhlaba okuqhubekayo eIndonesia, eli lizwe alinakukwazi ukumelana nengqumbo yendalo.
Ngoxa kwakhiwa iindawo zokukhusela iitsunami eAceh, azisoloko zikhona kwezinye iindawo.
Ukungabikho kwesilumkiso se-tsunami ePalu, nangona isilumkiso sasisetyenzisiwe, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kwaba negalelo ekulahlekeni kobomi.
Xa useluhambeni phakathi kweziqithi ezininzi zaseIndonesia, kuba nzima.
Iintlekele zemvelo zenza kube nzima ngakumbi ukuzilungiselela.
Inqanawa yesibhedlele eyayibekwe eLombok ukunyanga amaxhoba enyikima isendleleni eya ePalu, kodwa kuya kuthatha ubuncinane iintsuku ezintathu ukufikelela kwindawo yentlekele entsha.
UMongameli uJoko Widodo wenza ukuphuculwa kweziseko zengqala-mhlaba zaseIndonesia ezonakeleyo yaba yeyona nto iphambili kwiphulo lakhe lokhetho, yaye uye wachitha imali eninzi ekwakheni iindlela noololiwe.
Kodwa ulawulo lukaMnu. Joko luye lwabandezeleka ngenxa yokunqongophala kwemali njengoko ejongene nokunyulwa kwakhona kunyaka ozayo.
Kwakhona uMnu. Joko ujamelene nengcinezelo evela kwiingxabano zamahlelo aseIndonesia, apho amalungu ebutho lamaSilamsi aye amkela uhlobo oluthile lwenkolelo.
Kwabulawa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1.000 yaye amashumi amawaka ashiya amakhaya awo njengoko amaqela amaKrestu namaSilamsi ayesilwa ezitratweni, esebenzisa iimfanta, izaphetha nezinye izixhobo ezingekho mthethweni.
Bukela: UDaniel Sturridge waseLiverpool uthoba umlo wokulinganisa ngokunzulu neChelsea
UDaniel Sturridge usindise iLiverpool kwi-Premier League xa bebetha iChelsea ngomzuzu wama-89 ngoMgqibelo eStamford Bridge eLondon.
USturridge wafumana ipasi kuXherdan Shaqiri xa ebemalunga neeyadi ezingama-30 ukusuka kwigowuli leChelsea neqela lakhe lilandela ngo-1-0.
Wayibetha ibhola ekhohlo ngaphambi kokuba adubule ibhola ekwintsika ekude.
