Kuphume uphando lokubulawa komfazi emva kokufunyanwa kwesidumbu sakhe eBirkenhead, eMerseyside ngale ntsasa.
Indoda eneminyaka engama-44 ubudala yafunyanwa ngo-7: 55 kusasa ngamanxeba okuhlaba kwiGrayson Mews kwiJohn Street, kunye nendoda eneminyaka engama-32 ubudala ebanjwe ngokungathandabuzekiyo ngokubulala.
Amapolisa aye abongoza abantu abakwindawo ababone okanye beve into ethile ukuba bazise.
Umcuphi uMhloli uBrian O'Hagan uthe: 'Uphando lusekuqaleni kodwa ndingathanda ukubhenela nakubani na owayekwicala elikuJohn Street eBirkenhead owabona okanye weva into ekrokrisayo ukuba aqhagamshelane nathi.
