Ngoku abahlali baxelelwa ukuba kuza kuthatha iiyure ngaphambi kokuba bavunyelwe ukuba babuyele.
Elinye ipolisa liye laviwa lixelela enye indoda ukuba yonke le ndawo ngoku iphathwa njengendawo ekwenzeke kuyo ulwaphulo-mthetho.
Kwafika ibhinqa lilila kwindawo yesigameko.
Uhlala ephindaphinda esithi 'kakubi gqitha.'
