Umfanekiso kaCromwell wePalamente uba sisikhumbuzo esitsha esibethwe 'ngokubhala ngokutsha imbali'
Ukugxothwa kwayo bekuya kuba bubulungisa obuqhutywa ziimbongi ngenxa yokutshatyalaliswa kwezinto ezininzi zenkcubeko nezonqulo zaseNgilani ezenziwa ngabalandeli bakhe abafana namaTaliban.
Kodwa iCromwell Society yachaza icebiso likaMnu. Crick "njengobudenge" "nemizamo yokubhala imbali ngokutsha".
UJohn Goldsmith, ongusihlalo weCromwell Society, wathi: "Kwakungenakuphepheka kwimpikiswano ekhoyo ngokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo ukuba umfanekiso kaOliver Cromwell ngaphandle kweBhotwe laseWestminster wawuza kuba yinto ekujoliswe kuyo.
Iinkcaso zemfazwe yamakhaya eNgilani azizange ziyalelwe okanye zenziwe nguCromwell.
Mhlawumbi uCromwell ongalunganga wayeza kuxhelwa ngenxa yezenzo zokhokho wakhe uThomas kwinkulungwane engaphambili.
Umfanekiso omhle kaCromwell owenziwe nguSir William Hamo Thorneycroft ungqina iimbono zenkulungwane ye-19 yaye uyinxalenye yembali yomntu abaninzi abakholelwa ukuba ufanele ukubhiyozelwa.
UMnu Goldsmith waxelela iThe Sunday Telegraph wathi: "UCromwell ugqalwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ngakumbi ekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-19 kunanamhlanje, njengomkhuseli wepalamente ngokuchasene nengcinezelo yangaphandle, kwimeko yakhe yenkqubo yobukumkani.
Enoba oko kuyimbonakaliso echane ngokupheleleyo ngumbandela wentetho yomlando eqhubekayo.
Into esiqiniseke ngayo kukuba ungquzulwano olwenzeka phakathi kwenkulungwane ye-17 lwayichaza indlela oluya kuqhubeka lukhula ngayo uhlanga lwethu, yaye uCromwell ngumntu owaziwayo omela icala elinye laloo mahluko.
Iimpumelelo zakhe njengoMkhuseli oyiNkosi nazo zifanele zibhiyozelwe zize zikhunjulwe".
Iintsana Ezibulala Ihagu Umfama WaseTshayina Ufa
Ngokutsho kweendaba zasekuhlaleni, omnye umfama wahlaselwa waza wabulawa yingulube kwimarike ekumzantsi-ntshona weTshayina.
Iphephandaba iSouth China Morning Post lithi, le ndoda, eyaziwa ngegama layo kuphela elithi "Yuan", yafunyanwa ifile, inemithambo eyaphukileyo, igcwele igazi kufutshane nesitulo esisemarikeni eLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou.
Umlimi wehagu ulungiselela ukutofa amayeza okugonya kwihagu kwindawo yokufuya iihagu ngoMeyi 30, 2005 eXining kwiPhondo laseQinghai, eTshayina.
Kuthiwa lo mfana wayehambe nomzala wakhe besuka kwiphondo elingummelwane iYunnan ngoLwesithathu ukuya kuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 emarikeni.
Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana efile, waza wafumanisa umnyango wefama yehagu ekufutshane uvulekile.
Wathi kuloo ndlu kwakukho igxalaba elikhulu lehagu enegazi emlonyeni wayo.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo, uphando lwezomthetho lwangqina ukuba le ngulube ibimalunga neekhilogram ezingama - 550 yayimqwenge umfama de wafa.
Lo mzala, obizwa ngegama lakhe elithi "Wu", wathi, "imilenze yomzala wam yayiphalaza igazi yaye yonakele", njengoko icatshulwe kwiGuiyang Evening News.
Iifoto zekhamera yokhuseleko zibonise uYuan engena kwindawo yentengiso ngo-4:40 kusasa ngoLwesine ukuze ondle iihagu zakhe.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa emva kweyure.
Isilwanyana esabulala le ndoda sasingengowakwaYuan okanye esomzala wakhe.
Umphathi wentengiso waxelela iEvening News ukuba le ngulube yayivalelwe ukuze ingohluphi nabani na, ngoxa amapolisa ayeqokelela ubungqina kwindawo yesiganeko.
Intsapho kaYuan neziphathamandla zentengiso kuthiwa zixoxisana ngomvuzo wokufa kwakhe.
Nangona kunqabile, kuye kwabhalwa ngemeko yehagu ehlasela abantu ngaphambili.
Ngowe - 2016, ingulube yahlasela ibhinqa nomyeni walo kwifama yalo eMassachusetts, yaza yamshiya enzakele kakhulu.
Kwiminyaka elishumi eyadlulayo, ingulube enobunzima obuziikhilogram ezingama-650 yabethelela umfama waseWales kwitrektara yakhe de umfazi wakhe wayigxotha loo nkomo.
Emva kokuba umfama waseOregon etyiwe ziingulube zakhe ngo-2012, omnye umfama waseManitoba waxelela iCBC News ukuba iihagu azikho ngqwabalala kodwa ukunambitha igazi kunokubangela ukuba kube njalo.
"Badlala nje.
Zizigebenga, zifuna ukwazi kakhulu ... azenzanga nto imbi.
Kufuneka ubaphathe ngembeko efanelekileyo", utshilo.
Iintsalela zenkanyamba uRosa ziza kuzisa imvula enkulu ebanzi kumzantsi-ntshona we-US
Njengoko bekuxelwe kwangaphambili, iNkanyamba uRosa iya isiba buthathaka njengoko isondela kumanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, uRosa uza kuzisa izikhukula zemvula kumantla eMexico nakumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States kwiintsuku ezizayo.
URosa wayenomoya obetha ngesantya sama-85 ngeyure, iNkanyamba yoDidi 1, ukususela ngo-5 kusasa ngexesha lasempuma ngeCawa, yaye ibikumgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-385 kumazantsi-ntshona ePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa ahambe aye emntla ngeCawa.
Okwangoku, kukho umjikelo osondela ngaselwandle lwePasifiki uze usinge ngasempuma ukuya kwiNxweme eseNtshona yaseUnited States. Njengoko uRosa esondela kwiBaja California ngoMvulo njengesaqhwithi esiyingozi, uza kuqalisa ukutyhala amanzi ashushu ashushu ashushu emantla ukuya kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States.
URosa uza kuzisa iimvula ezifikelela kwii-intshi ezili-10 kwimimandla ethile yaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, umswakama wendawo eshushu oza kunxibelelana nomlambo osondelayo uza kubangela imvula eninzi kwicala eliseMzantsi Ntshona kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Kwindawo ethile, imvula enokuba zii-intshi ezi-1 ukuya kwezi-4 iza kubangela izikhukula eziyingozi, imvula eninzi kunye nokukhukuliseka komhlaba kwintlango.
Umkhenkce onzulu wemozulu yelizwe elishushu uza kubangela ukuba imvula ibe zii-intshi ezimbini ukuya kwezintathu ngeyure kwiindawo ezithile, ingakumbi kwimimandla esemazantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kulindeleke ukuba kubekho iimvula ezifikelela kwii-intshi ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-4 kwiindawo ezithile ezikumzantsi-ntshona, ingakumbi kwiArizona.
Izikhukula ezinokwenzeka zinokubangela ukuba iimeko zonakele ngokukhawuleza ngenxa yemvula yeetropiki.
Bekungayi kuba bubulumko kakhulu ukubhadula entlango ngeenyawo xa kukho isoyikiso semvula etshisayo.
Imvula enkulu inokubangela ukuba imiwonyo ibe yimilambo eqhumayo yaye iziphango ziya kuzisa imimoya enesiphango neenduli ezinothuli.
Le ngxangxasi iza kuzisa imvula eninzi kwiindawo ezithile kunxweme lwaseMzantsi California.
Imvula enokubakho ingafikelela kwiintshi ezintlanu, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba kubekho imfumba yenkunkuma kunye neendlela ezibuthelezi.
Le yayiza kuba yimvula yokuqala kule ngingqi ebudeni bexesha lemvula.
Ezinye iimvula ezichithakeleyo ziya kuqala ukufikelela eArizona ekupheleni kweCawa nasekuqaleni koMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula ibe nkulu ngoMvulo nangeLwesibini.
Imvula enkulu iya kunetha kwiiNdawo ezine ngoLwesibini ize iqhubeke de kube ngoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha kunokubakho amaqondo obushushu atshintshatshintshayo kulo lonke elaseUnited States njengoko iArctic iba shushu, kodwa iindawo ezishushu zihlala zishushu.
Ngamanye amaxesha oku kukhokelela kutshintsho olukhulu kubushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Kukho umzekelo omhle womahluko wobushushu obalaseleyo kumbindi weUnited States ngeCawa.
Kukho umahluko wamaqondo obushushu amalunga nama - 20 ngokukaCelsius phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, naphakathi kweSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu obuhlala buhleli behlobo buza kuzama ukwakha buze bandise kwakhona.
Kwinxalenye enkulu kumbindi nasempuma ye-US kulindeleke ukuba kubekho ukufudumala ekuqaleni kuka-Oktobha, apho amaqondo obushushu aya kuma kwi-80 ukusuka kwiiNtaba zaseMazantsi ukuya kwiindawo ezithile kuMntla-mpuma.
Isixeko saseNew York sinokufikelela kuma-80 ngokukaCelsius ngoLwesibini, nto leyo eya kuba malunga nama-10 ngokukaCelsius ngaphezu komndilili.
Ingxelo yethu yezulu yexesha elide ibonisa ukuba kusenokwenzeka ukuba imozulu yemozulu ibe ngaphezu komlinganiselo wobushushu obuqhelekileyo kwimpuma yeUnited States de kube sisiqingatha sokuqala sika-Oktobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukela ukuchotshelwa kwetyala likaBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ubungqina obothusayo ngoLwesine obenziwa ngummeli weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh kunye nebhinqa elimtyhola ngokuhlaselwa ngokwesini ekuthiwa kwenzeka ngeminyaka yee-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford, kwiinkqubo ezintandathu zikamabonwakude.
Kwangaxeshanye, kwaqhubeka ukungavisisani kwezopolitiko, abasasazi bephazamisa inkqubo yabo yesiqhelo ngoLwesihlanu ngomzuzu wokugqibela: isivumelwano esenziwe ngugqirha waseArizona uJeff Flake sokuba iFBI yenze uphando lweveki enye lwaloo mabango.
UFord waxelela iKomiti yeNkundla yeNdlu yeeNgwevu ukuba uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba uKavanaugh wamchukumisa enxilile waza wazama ukumkhulula iimpahla zakhe kwitheko lesikolo samabanga aphakamileyo.
UKavanaugh, kwingxelo yakhe enenzondelelo, wathi uqinisekile nge-100 pesenti ukuba akuzange kwenzeke.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20.4 abaxelwe nguNielsen ngoLwesihlanu bayibukele.
Le nkampani yayibalisa umlinganiselo wababukeli kwii - CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel neMSNBC.
Amanani awazange afumaneke ngoko nangoko kwamanye amanethiwekhi awayibonisa, kuquka iPBS, iC-SPAN neFox Business Network.
Yaye uNelson udla ngokuba nengxaki yokulinganisa abantu ababukela kwiiofisi.
Ukubeka oko ngenye indlela, oko kukuthi, abantu ababukeleyo bafana nabo babekho kwimidlalo yebhola ekhatywayo okanye kwii-Academy Awards.
I-Fox News Channel, eneenkqubo ezixhasa ngokuthe ngqo ukumiselwa kukaKavanaugh, ikhokele zonke iinkqubo nge-avareji yezigidi ezi-5.69 ababukeli ebudeni bemini yokuva, utshilo uNielsen.
IABC yayikwindawo yesibini nge-3.26 lezigidi zababukeli.
I-CBS yayinezigidi ezi-3.1, i-NBC yayinazo izigidi ezi-2.94, i-MSNBC yayinazo izigidi ezi-2.89 yaye i-CNN yayinazo izigidi ezi-2.52 ngokutsho kukaNielsen.
Inzala yahlala iphezulu emva kokuvalelwa.
UFlake wayengumntu ophambili kwidrama yangoLwesihlanu.
Emva kokuba iofisi kaRhulumente elungeleleneyo ikhuphe ingxelo yokuba uza kuvotela uKavanaugh, wabanjwa kwiikhamera zeCNN neCBS ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu ekhwazwa ngabadla-ndlebe njengoko wayezama ukukhwela ikheshi ukuya kwintlanganiso yeKomiti yezoBulungisa.
Wema ngamehlo athe khunubembe imizuzu eliqela njengoko wayegxekwa, ekhutshelwa ngqo kumabonwakude kwi-CNN.
Elinye ibhinqa lathi: "Ndikho kanye apha phambi kwakho".
"Ngaba ucinga ukuba uthetha inyaniso kwilizwe?
Waxelelwa ukuba, "unamandla xa uninzi lwabafazi lungenamandla".
UFlake wathi iofisi yakhe ikhuphe ingxelo yaye wathi, ngaphambi kokuba ivale ikheshi, wayeza kuthetha okungakumbi ekuveni ikomiti.
Iinkqubo zekhebula nezonxibelelwano zonke zazisasaza ngokuthe ngqo emva kweeyure, xa iKomiti yezoBulungisa yayiza kuvota ukuqhubela phambili ukonyulwa kukaKavanaugh kwiNdlu epheleleyo yeNgingqi ukuze kuvotelwe.
Kodwa uFlake wathi wayeza kukwenza oko kuphela xa eqonda ukuba i-FBI iza kuhlolisisa izityholo ezibhekiswe kulo mgqatswa kwiveki ezayo, nto leyo eye yanconywa ngamaDemokhrasi amancinane.
UFlake waqiniseka ngenxa yokuncokola nomhlobo wakhe, uCons.
Emva kokuthetha noCoons kunye neesenethi eziliqela emva koko, uFlake wenza isigqibo sakhe.
Ukhetho lukaFlake lwalunamandla, kuba kwakucacile ukuba amaRiphabliki ayengasayi kuba neevoti zokuvuma uKavanaugh ngaphandle kophando.
UMongameli uTrump uvule uphando lwe-FBI kwizityholo ezichasene noKavanaugh.
