I-Wayde Sims shooting: Amapolisa abamba umrhanelwa uDyteon Simpson ngokufa komdlali we-LSU
Amapolisa abambe umrhanelwa ngokudubula uWayde Sims, umdlali webhasikithi oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala kwiLSU.
UDyteon Simpson, oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala, ubanjiwe waza wabekwa ityala lokubulala ngokungenangqiqo, ngokutsho kweSebe lamaPolisa laseBaton Rouge.
Amagosa akhupha ividiyo yomlo phakathi kukaSims noSimpson, yaye amapolisa athi uSims walahlekelwa ziiglasi zakhe ebudeni bomlo.
Amapolisa afumana iiglasi kwindawo yesigameko aza athi afumene iDNA kaSimpson kuzo, ingxelo yeWFB yeCBS.
Emva kokubuza imibuzo kuSimpson, amapolisa athi uvumile ukuba wadubula uWayde.
Ingxelo yeAdvocate ithi ibhondi yakhe iye yabekwa kwi-$350,000.
Kwiofisi yoMgwebi wezifo zengqondo yaseMpuma Baton Rouge Parish, ngoLwesihlanu, kuye kwapapashwa ingxelo yokuqala, isithi unobangela wokufa yintloko ehlabeke entanyeni.
Isebe libulela iqela eliphandayo lamapolisa aseLouisiana, isebe lamapolisa eliphangela, amapolisa eSouthern University kunye nabemi bendawo ngokuncedisa kuphando olukhokelela ekubanjweni.
UMlawuli wezemidlalo weLSU uJoe Alleva ubulele abasemagunyeni "ngenzondelelo yabo nokwenza kwabo ubulungisa".
USims wayeneminyaka engama-20 ubudala.
Lo mdlali uphakame kakhulu wakhulela eBaton Rouge, apho uyise, uWayne, naye wayedlala khona ibhola yomnyazi kwiLSU.
Wayenomlinganiselo weenqaku ezi-5.6 kunye ne-2.6 yokubuyisela umdlalo omnye kunyaka ophelileyo.
NgoLwesihlanu kusasa, umqeqeshi webhasikiti weLSU uWill Wade uthe iqela "libuhlungu kakhulu" kwaye "libuhlungu" kukufa kukaWayde.
"Yiyo le nto uhlala uxhalabile ngayo", watsho njalo uWade.
