Abantu abathandathu babanjwa eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo emva kokuba abaqhankqalazi abaxhasa inkululeko bebhenele kumapolisa, kwaye amawaka-waka abantu beye bathelekisa abaqhankqalazi ababethelekisa ukubonisa isikhumbuzo sokuqala sokuvota kweCatalonia.
Iqela labantu ababenxibe iimaski ababencedisa amaqela abo babetha ngeqanda baza babetha ngepeyinti, besenza amafu amnyama othuli ezitratweni ebeziqhele ukuzala ziindwendwe.
Kamva ngaloo mini kwaqhambuka umlo, amapolisa asebenzisa imijukujelwa yawo ukuze athintele loo ngxabano.
Kangangeeyure eziliqela amaqela alwela inkululeko ayesithi "Akukho kulibala, akukho kuxolelwa" ajamelana nabaqhankqalazi beqela elidibanisayo ababekhwaza, "Makaphile iSpeyin".
Ngokwabapapashi basekuhlaleni, abantu abalishumi elinesine baye banyangwa ngenxa yokwenzakala okuncinane abafumene kwiimvavanyo.
Uxinzelelo lwanda kwingingqi efuna ukuzimela, emva konyaka kwenzeke intetho-zimvo ngo-Oktobha 1 eyayigqalwa ingekho mthethweni yiMadrid kodwa yabhiyozelwa ngabantu baseCatalan abafuna ukwahlukana.
Abavoti bakhetha kakhulu ukuba bazimele, nangona ukuvota kwakuncinci kunye nabo bachasene nokuvota ngokubanzi.
Ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni baseCatalan, abantu abamalunga ne-1000 baye bonzakala kunyaka ophelileyo emva kokuba amapolisa ezame ukuphazamisa ukuvota kwiindawo zokuvota kulo lonke elo phondo ngethuba leengxabano ezinogonyamelo.
Amaqela alwela inkululeko aye amise inkampu ebusuku ngoLwesihlanu ukuze athintele umboniso wokuxhasa amapolisa kazwelonke.
Le ntlanganiso yaqhubeka kodwa kwanyanzeleka ukuba ithathe enye indlela.
UNarcis Termes, 68, osisazi sombane owayekho kunye nomfazi wakhe kwimbambano yokuzimela geqe, wathi akasenawo nethemba lokuba iCatalan iya kuba lizimele geqe.
"Kunyaka ophelileyo siye safumana elinye lamathuba amyoli.
Ndibabone abazali bam belila luvuyo xa bekwazile ukuvota kodwa ngoku sivaleleke", utshilo.
Nangona bephumelele ngempumelelo enkulu kulonyulo lwengingqi olwenzeke kwinyanga ephelileyo kaDisemba, amaqela aseCatalan axhasa ukuzimela-geqe aye alwa nzima ukuqhubeka nokukhuthaza lo nyaka, uninzi lwawona madoda aziwayo aziinkokeli zawo, mhlawumbi eziqweqwe okanye ezivalelwe, belindele ukuxoxwa kwetyala ngenxa yendima yabo ekuququzeleleni intetho-zonke nokubhengezwa kwenkululeko.
UJoan Puig, umlungisi wemoto oneminyaka engama-42 ubudala, owayeqweqwe umngcelele wokuxhasa amapolisa, wathi le ngxabano yayibangelwa ngabezopolitiko bamacala omabini.
Wathi: "Iba nzima nangakumbi".
NgoMgqibelo, uOriol Junqueras, omnye wabakhokeli abasithoba baseCatalan abasentolongweni ukususela ekupheleni konyaka ophelileyo, wabhengeza ukuba uza kuba kwiphulo lokhetho lwePalamente yaseYurophu kunyaka ozayo.
