Lo kaLee, unencwadi ethi "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" epapashwe kule nyanga yiHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, ungumphathi we-Sinovation Ventures, eye yatyala imali kwenye yeenkampani ze-AI eziphambili eChina, i-Face++.
Ngeminyaka yee-1980 kwiYunivesithi yaseCarnegie Mellon wasebenza kwinkqubo yeAI eyayibetha oyena mdlali ubalaseleyo waseMelika uOthello, kwaye kamva waba ngumphathi kwiMicrosoft Research kunye nomongameli wesebe laseGoogle eChina.
ULee wavuma ukuba ukhuphiswano lwezixhobo zeteknoloji olwalusenziwa ngurhulumente waseUnited States ngaphambili, njengohlobo lweDefense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge, luza kubakho nini olandelayo, ukuze kuncedwe ekuchongeni ababonisi abaza kubakho.
