John Edward: Ulwazi lweelwimi lubalulekile kubemi behlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zigcina ingxelo yokugqwesa kwizifundo, kwaye oku kuqhubeke ngo-2018 ngesinye iseti yeziphumo ezibalaseleyo zeemviwo, eziqiniswe kuphela yimpumelelo yomntu ngamnye kunye neqela kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo kunye neminye imizamo yoluntu.
Ngaphezulu kwabafundi abangama-30 000 eScotland, ezi zikolo, zimelwe yiBhunga laseScotland leZikolo eziZimeleyo (SCIS), zizama ukubonelela ngeyona nkonzo ilungileyo kubafundi nabazali bazo.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zijolise ekulungiseleleni abafundi bazo kwimfundo eyongezelelweyo neyomgangatho ophezulu, umsebenzi wabo abawukhethileyo kunye nendawo yabo njengabemi behlabathi.
Njengomzi mveliso wemfundo onokwakha uphinde uphumeze inkqubo yesikolo esenzelwe ngokwezifiso, sibona iilwimi zale mihla ziqhubeka njengesifundo esithandwayo nesifunwayo ezikolweni.
UNelson Mandela wathi: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi aluqondayo, luyaphuma olo lwimi luye entlokweni yakhe.
Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe, oko kuya kufikelela intliziyo yakhe".
Esi sisikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuba asinakuthembela kwisiNgesi kuphela xa sifuna ukwakha ulwalamano nokuthembana nabantu abavela kwamanye amazwe.
Ngokutsho kweziphumo zeemviwo zalo nyaka, sinokubona ukuba iilwimi ziphezulu kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.
I-68% yabafundi abafunda iilwimi zasemzini bafumana iBakala A.
Iinkcukacha eziqokelelwe kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezingamalungu eSCIS, zibonisa ukuba ama-72 ekhulwini abafundi bafumana iBakala A eliPhezulu kwisiMandarin, ngelixa ama-72 ekhulwini abo bafunda isiJamani, ama-69 ekhulwini abo bafunda isiFrentshi nama-63 ekhulwini abo bafunda iSpanish nabo bafumana iBakala A.
Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eScotland zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo abantwana nolutsha oluya kuthi ngokungathandabuzekiyo luzifune kwixesha elizayo.
Iilwimi ngoku, njengento ekhethiweyo, zibekwa kwindawo enye nezifundo ze-STEM (isayensi, iteknoloji, ubunjineli nemathematika) kwizifundo ezizimeleyo zesikolo nakwezinye iindawo.
Uhlolisiso olwenziwe yiKomishoni yase-UK yeNgqesho neZakhono ngo-2014 lwafumanisa ukuba kwezizathu abazinikiweyo ngabaqeshi zokungafumani umsebenzi, i-17 ekhulwini lalithiwe linxulunyaniswa nokungabikho kwezakhono zolwimi.
Ngoko ke, ngokuthe chatha, izakhono zolwimi ziya zifuneka ukuze ulungiselele ulutsha kumsebenzi walo wexesha elizayo.
Ngenxa yokuba amathuba emisebenzi engakumbi efuna ulwimi, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi elidibeneyo.
Nokuba umntu ukhetha ukwenza ntoni na, ukuba ufunde ulwimi lwesibini, uya kuba nelungelo lokwenene kwixesha elizayo ukuba nolwazi olunjalo ubomi bakhe bonke.
Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu abavela kumazwe angaphandle kuya kwenza umntu othetha iilwimi ezininzi abe phambili kukhuphiswano.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwa nguYouGov kubantu abangaphezu kwama-4 000 abakhulileyo base-UK ngo-2013, i-75% ayikwazanga ukuthetha ulwimi lwasemzini ngokwaneleyo ukuze ibe nengxoxo kwaye isiFrentshi kuphela kolwimi oluthethwayo ngepesenti eneenombolo eziphindwe kabini, i-15%.
Yiyo loo nto ukubeka imali ekufundiseni ulwimi ngoku kubalulekile kubantwana banamhlanje.
Ukuba neelwimi ezininzi, ngokukodwa ezo zezoqoqosho ezisakhulayo, kuya kunceda abantwana babe namathuba angakumbi okufumana umsebenzi onentsingiselo.
IScotland, isikolo ngasinye siya kwahluka kwiilwimi ezifundisayo.
Ezinye izikolo ziza kugxininisa kwiilwimi zanamhlanje, ngoxa ezinye ziza kufundisa iilwimi ezijongwa njengezona zibalulekileyo e-UK xa kujongwa phambili ku-2020, ezifana nesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Enoba umntwana wakho unomdla phi, uya kusoloko enolwimi oluninzi anokukhetha phakathi kwalo kwizikolo ezizimeleyo, ezinengcali eziqeqeshekileyo kule nkalo.
