ULeBron uza kwenza iLakers idlale okokuqala ngeCawe eSan Diego
Ulindelo luphelile kubaxhasi abafuna ukubona uLeBron James eqala ukudlala kwiLos Angeles Lakers.
Umqeqeshi weLakers uLuke Walton uye wabhengeza ukuba uJames uza kudlala kumdlalo wokuvula wexesha lonyaka eliza kuba ngeCawa nxamnye neDenver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Kodwa ke akukabonakali ukuba iza kudlala yimalini.
"Kuya kuba ngaphezu kwe-1 nangaphantsi kwe-48", watsho uWalton kwiwebhsayithi esemthethweni yeLakers.
Iphephandaba leLakers uMike Trudell uthe kwiTwitter uJames uza kudlala imizuzu embalwa.
Emva kokuzilolonga ekuqaleni kwale veki, uJames wabuzwa malunga nezicwangciso zakhe zokuba iLakers idlale imidlalo emithandathu ngaphambi kwexesha lonyaka.
"Andifuni midlalo yexesha langaphambili kweli nqanaba lomsebenzi wam ukuze ndikulungele", utshilo.
Ixesha leNgqungquthela yaseNtshona Virginia kaTrump, i-YouTube Channel
UMongameli uDonald Trump uqalisa umngcelele weentlanganiso zokunyusa umkhosi namhlanje eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia.
Le yindawo yokuqala kwezintlanu ezicwangciselwe uTump kwiveki ezayo, kuquka ukuyeka kwiindawo ezithandwayo kuquka iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngokuvotelwa kokuqinisekiswa kokhetho lwakhe lokuzalisa isithuba seNkundla ePhakamileyo, uTrump ujonge ukwakha inkxaso kunyulo oluzayo phakathi kwexesha kuba iiRiphablikhi zisengozini yokulahlekelwa lulawulo lweCongress xa kuvotwa ngoNovemba.
Inini intlanganiso kaTrump eNtshona Virginia ngokuhlwanje yaye uyibukela njani kwi-intanethi?
Iintlanganiso zikaTrump eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia zicwangciselwe ukuba zibe ngentsimbi yesi-7 ebusuku, ngoMgqibelo, Septemba 29, 2018.
Unokuyibukela intlanganiso kaTrump eWest Virginia nge-intanethi ngezantsi nge-YouTube.
UTrump kusenokwenzeka ukuba uza kuthetha ngeentetho eziza kuthethwa kule veki kumgqatswa weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh, eziye zathintelwa ngenxa yezityholo zokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesini kunye nokuvota kwangaphambili kokuqinisekiswa kweSenate ebekwe ecaleni kangangeveki ngelixa iFBI iphengulula.
Kodwa eyona njongo yale mibhiyozo yokunikela uncedo kukubanceda abantu baseRiphabliki abajongene nokhetho lwangoNovemba ukuba bafumane amandla.
Ngokutsho kwe-Reuters, iqela likaMongameli uTrump likhankanyile ukuba le mitshato mihlanu kwiveki ezayo ijolise "ekuvuseleleni amavolontiya kunye nabaxhasi njengoko amaRiphabhliki ezama ukukhusela nokwandisa izikhundla zawo kwiNdlu yoWiso-mthetho kunye neNdlu yabameli".
"Ulawulo lweCongress lubaluleke kakhulu kwi-ajenda yakhe kangangokuba umongameli uza kuhamba ukuya kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko njengoko singena kwisizini yomkhankaso exakekileyo", isithethi somkhankaso kaTrump esala ukubizwa ngegama laso sixelele iReuters.
Umnyhadala wolu suku, ocwangciselwe ukuba ube kwiWesbanco Arena eWheeling, unokubangela ukuba kubekho abaxhasi "beOhio nasePennsylvania baze bafumane inkcazelo kumajelo eendaba asePittsburgh", ngokutsho kweWest Virginia Metro News.
NgoMgqibelo iya kuba sisihlandlo sesibini kwinyanga ephelileyo apho uTrump etyelele iWest Virginia, ilizwe elo aliphumeleleyo ngamanqaku angaphezulu kwama-40 ekhulwini ngo-2016.
UTrump uzama ukunceda umviwa weRiphabliki uPatrick Morrisey, ongenela i-West Virginia, ongena kwimboni.
USimon Haeder, isazinzulu kwezopolitiko kwiYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, uthi: "Asikokunika themba lokuba uMorissey uza kuza kuzama ukumkhuthaza".
I-Ryder Cup 2018: Iqela lase-USA libonisa isisu sokulwa ukuze ligcine amathemba ephila liza kungena kwi-singles yangeCawa
Emva kweentlanganiso ezintathu ezinamacala amabini, iziganeko zentsimbi yesine ngoMgqibelo emva kwemini zisenokuba zezo zifunekayo kwiNdebe yeRyder.
I-swinging pendulum of momentum ingumbono wezemidlalo owenziwe ngokupheleleyo kodwa lowo abadlali bakholelwa ngokwenene kuwo, yaye hayi ngakumbi xa bekhuphisana njengale.
Ngoko ke, baza kuthi yintoni intshukumo ngoku?
"Baye baphambili ngamanqaku amathandathu kwaye ngoku bane, ngoko ke siyakuthwala oko njengento encinane yokuqhutywa ndicinga ukuba", utshilo uJordan Spieth njengoko wayezihambela imini yonke.
IYurophu inexabiso, ngokucacileyo, ngamaphuzu amane phambi kwelo neephuzu ezilishumi elinesibini ezongezelelweyo.
AmaMerika, njengoko uSpieth esitsho, avakalelwa kukuba anomoya omncinci kwiiseyile zawo kwaye anokuninzi okunokubakhuthaza, ingakumbi uhlobo lukaSpieth noJustin Thomas abadlale kunye imini yonke kwaye ngamnye unamanqaku amathathu kwabane.
USpieth ebesidla ngendeb' eqhaza ukususela kwithe ukuya kwi-green kwaye uyabakhokela ngokwenza umzekelo.
Loo mazwi omngxala wokuvuyela ayeya esiba mandundu njengoko umjikelo wakhe wawusiya phambili, elahla i-putt ebalulekileyo ukuze athabathe umdlalo wesine xa yena noThomas beye behla kabini emva kweemibini.
Ukubetha kwakhe iqhosha elibaphumeleleyo kumdlalo we-15 kwafumana ukhwaza okufanayo, uhlobo olukuxelela ukuba ukholelwa ukuba iqela laseMerika alikho ngaphandle koku.
"Umele nje ukhangele nzulu uze uxhalabele umdlalo wakho", watsho uSpieth.
Yiyo yonke le nto nganye yabadlali abaseleyo ngoku.
Iimbobo ezili-18 zokwenza uphawu.
Abona badlali banamanqaku amaninzi kunoSpieth noThomas kwiintsuku ezimbini ezidlulileyo nguFrancesco Molinari noTommy Fleetwood, ibali elingenakuphikiswa leRyder Cup.
Isibini esingaqhelekanga kodwa esimnandi saseYurophu sinezihlandlo ezine kwii-4 yaye asinakwenza nto iphosakeleyo.
"Moliwood" yayikukuphela kweqela elingazange lidubule ibhogi emva kwemini ngoMgqibelo, kodwa kwakhona lalikuphepha ukudubula ibhogi kusasa ngoMgqibelo, emva kwemini ngoLwesihlanu nangentsimbi yesithoba ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu.
Loo nto, nendlela amandla abo abonakala ehla ngayo esi sihlwele singxolayo, iqinisekisa ukuba ngabadlali abaza koyisa ngeCawa, yaye akakho umdlali odumileyo oza kunika uloyiso oluya kwenzeka eYurophu njengoko ilanga litshona kwiLe Golf National ngaphezu kukaFleetwood okanye uMolinari.
Ngcono zombini ngaxeshanye kwimingxuma eyahlukeneyo.
Noko ke, ukuthetha ngozuko lwaseYurophu kusekulithuba.
UBubba Watson noWebb Simpson bamenza umsebenzi omfutshane uSergio Garcia, iqhawe leebhola ezine zentsasa, xa wadityaniswa noAlex Noren.
I-bogey kunye namabini amabini kwicala langaphambili eli-9 abemba umSpanish nomSweden kumngxuma abangazange basondele ekuphumeni kuwo.
Noko ke, ngeCawa, akukho mntu uya kukunceda uphume emngxunyeni wakho.
Iibhola ezine kunye neqela leqela leqela ezine zinomdla kakhulu ukuba zibonwe ngokusondeleyo ngenxa yokunxibelelana phakathi kwezibini, iingcebiso ezizinikayo, iingcebiso ezingazinikayo nendlela isicwangciso esinokutshintsha ngayo ngephanyazo.
IYurophu idlale kakuhle njengeqela ukuza kuthi ga ngoku kwaye ithatha indawo ephambili kumhla wokugqibela kodwa le seshoni yeqela leqela leqela liye labonisa ukuba iTeam USA inesisu sokulwa abanye, ingakumbi i-Stateside, bebeyithandabuza.
IYurophu ithatha 10-6 ikhokele kumhla wokugqibela weRyder Cup
IYurophu iza kuba nelungelo elikhulu kumdlalo wokugqibela weRyder Cup emva kokuphumelela kwimidlalo yeebhola ezine neeyayi ezine ngoMgqibelo, ikhokele iUnited States ngo-10-6.
Iqela elibini elinomdla uTommy Fleetwood noFrancesco Molinari liyakhokela ngokuloba kabini kwiTiger Woods elwisana nobunzima ukuze lifikelele kwamanqaku amane kwiLe Golf National.
Iqela laseYurophu likaThomas Bjorn, elalifuna ukugcina indebe elaliyishiyile eHazeltine kwiminyaka emibini edluleyo, lalawula iqela laseMerika elaliphulukana neembasa ezine ekuseni, laza laphumelela umdlalo ngo-3-1.
I-US yabonelela ngonyamezelo olungakumbi kwiiquartets, iphumelele imidlalo emibini, kodwa ayikwazanga ukondla umngeni.
Iqela likaJim Furyk lifuna amanqaku asibhozo kwimidlalo elishumi elinesibini yobusuku bangeCawa ukuze lifumane indebe.
UFleetwood ngowokuqala kwe-Europe ukuphumelela amanqaku amane alandelelanayo lo gama yena noMolinari, obizwa ngokuba "nguMolliwood" emva kwempelaveki emnandi, besesibini ukuphumelela amanqaku amane kwimidlalo yabo emine yokuqala kwimbali yeNdebe yeRyder.
Emva kokugqogqa uWoods noPatrick Reed kwii-fourballs, babetha ngokumangalisayo ukubetha uWoods no-Bryson Dechambeau, i-rookie yase-US, nge-5 kunye ne-4.
UWoods, owatsala nzima kwimidlalo emibini ngoMgqibelo, wabonakalisa ubuchule bakhe ngamanye amaxesha kodwa ngoku uphulukene nemidlalo engama-19 kwezingama-29 ebezibukele kwiiququ kunye neezine kunye nesixhenxe ngokulandelelana.
UJustin Rose, ophumleleyo kwimidlalo yentsasa ye-fourballs, ubuyele kwiqabane lakhe uHenrik Stenson kwimidlalo ye-fourballs ukuze oyise u-Dustin Johnson no-Brooks Koepka ngo-2 no-1 - abekwe kwindawo yokuqala nesithathu kwihlabathi.
IYurophu ayizange iyenze ngokwayo nangona kusemini emnandi, enomoya kumazantsi-ntshona eParis.
I-Jordan Spieth neJustin Thomas abaphumelele imidlalo emikhulu kathathu, babeka umgangatho kumaMerika ngamanqaku amabini ngoMgqibelo.
Bafumana i 2 & 1 ye 2 & 1 kwi-Spain Jon Rahm kunye ne-Ian Poulter kwi-fourballs kwaye babuyela emva koko ukubetha uPoulter noRory McIlroy 4 & 3 kwi-foursomes belahlekelwe yimingxuma emibini yokuvula.
Kuphela kube kabini kwimbali yeRyder Cup iqela libuye emva kokungaphumeleli ngamanqaku amane ukuya kwimidlalo yokudlala, nangona njengamaqela aphetheyo iqela likaFuryk lifuna ukudweba ukuze lifumane indebe.
Noko ke, emva kokuba ngabona bantu babesiba nowona mgangatho uphezulu kwiintsuku ezimbini, ukuhlasela kwabo ngeCawa kubonakala ngathi akuyi kuba lula kubo.
I-North Korea ithi 'akukho ndlela' iya kuphelisa izixhobo ngaxeshanye ngaphandle kokuthembana
UMphathiswa wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba ukuqhubeka kwezohlwayo kuyaluphelisa ungathembelani eUnited States yaye akukho ndlela yokuba eli lizwe liziyeke ngokwalo izixhobo zenyukliya phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo.
URi Yong Ho waxelela iNtlanganiso Yonyaka kaZwelonke yequmrhu lehlabathi ukuba iNyakatho Korea yathabatha "amanyathelo abalulekileyo okwenza okulungileyo" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanywa kweenqwelo-mkhosi, ukudiliza indawo yovavanyo lwenyukliya, nokuthembisa ukungazisasazi izixhobo zenyukliya neteknoloji yenyukliya.
Wathi: "Kodwa, asifumani mpendulo ivela eUnited States".
"Ngaphandle kokuthembela kwi-U.S. akukho themba kukhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe kwaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo akukho ndlela yokuba singazikhulula ngokwethu kuqala".
Nangona uRi ephinda izikhalazo eziqhelekileyo zaseMntla Korea malunga nokumelana kweWashington "ngezigaba" indlela yokulahla izixhobo zenyukliya apho uMntla Korea uya kuvuzwa njengoko ethathe amanyathelo ngokuthe ngcembe, ingxelo yakhe ibonakala ibalulekile kuba ayizange iyigatye into yokulahla izixhobo zenyukliya ngokungathandabuzekiyo njengoko iPyongyang yenzile ngaphambili.
URi wayebhekisela kwingxelo eyayivunywe nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwintlanganiso yokuqala phakathi komongameli wase-US kunye nenkokeli yaseMntla Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12, xa uKim wathembisa ukusebenza "ekususeni izixhobo zenyukliya kwisiqithi saseKorea" ngelixa uTrump wathembisa iziqinisekiso zokhuseleko lwaseMntla Korea.
INorth Korea ibifuna ukuphelisa ngokusesikweni iMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States ithe iPyongyang ifanele iqale iyeke izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington iye yakwala ukucetyiswa kokunciphisa imiqathango yehlabathi kwiNorth Korea.
U-Ri wathi: "I-US igxininisa "kwinto yokuqala yokungabikho kwezikrweqe" yaye yandisa umlinganiselo woxinezeleko ngezohlwayo ukuze iphumeze injongo yayo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, yaye ide iyigatye "ingxelo yokuphela kwemfazwe".
"Ingcamango yokuba isohlwayo sinokusenza siguqe ngamadolo iphupha nje labantu abangenalo ulwazi ngathi.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba ukuqhubeka kwezihlwayo kusenza singathembani".
URi akazange athethe ngeengqungquthela ezicwangcisiweyo phakathi kukaKim noTrump ezithi umongameli wase-US wazigqamisa kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kweveki.
Kunoko, lo mphathiswa wathetha ngeentlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim nomlawuli waseMzantsi Korea uMoon Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo waza wongezelela wathi: "Ukuba ibinguMzantsi Korea, kungekhona iUnited States, ebekungekho nto injalo ngeKorea".
Nangona kunjalo, indlela uRi athetha ngayo yahluke kakhulu kuleyo wayethetha ngayo kunyaka ophelileyo, xa wayexelela iNtlanganiso Jikelele yeZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ukuba ukuhlasela ilizwe laseMelika ngemijukujelwa yaseMntla Korea kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba "uMnu. uMongameli ongendawo" uTrump ebize uKim "njengomntu wombhobho" owenza umsebenzi wokuzibulala.
Kulo nyaka kwiZizwe Ezimanyeneyo, uTrump, owawusongela "ukutshabalalisa" iNorth Korea kunyaka ophelileyo, wancoma uKim ngesibindi sakhe sokuthatha amanyathelo okunciphisa izixhobo, kodwa wathi kusekuninzi ekusafuneka kwenziwe kwaye izohlwayo kufuneka zihlale zikhona de iNorth Korea yenze i-denuclearizes.
NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathi akanalo ixesha elifanelekileyo lokuwenza oku, esithi "Nokuba kungathatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu - akunamsebenzi".
I-China neRashiya zithi iBhunga Lokhuseleko leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo lifanele liwuvuze iPyongyang ngamanyathelo eliwathathileyo.
Noko ke, uNobhala Welizwe LaseUnited States uMike Pompeo waxelela iBhunga Lokhuseleko leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoLwesine ukuba: "Ukunyanzeliswa kwezohlwayo zeBhunga Lokhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngamandla yaye kungaze kusilele de sifeze ngokupheleleyo, ekugqibeleni, ukuyekiswa kweentolo zenyukliya".
IBhunga loKhuseleko liye laqinisa ngazwi linye izohlwayo kwilizwe laseMntla Korea ukususela ngowama-2006 lizama ukucima imali yokuxhasa ngeenkqubo zenyukliya nezikhali ezihlasela umhlaba zePyongyang.
UPompeo wadibana noRi ngaphesheya kwegumbi lentlanganiso yeNdibano Jikelele yeZizwe Ezimanyeneyo waza wathi emva koko wayeza kuphinda atyelele iPyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukuze alungiselele intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo utyelele i-North Korea izihlandlo ezithathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugqibela aluzange luhambe kakuhle.
Washiya iPyongyang ngoJulayi esithi kubekho inkqubela, kodwa iNyakatho Korea yamgxeka emva kweeyure ezimbalwa ngenxa yokwenza "iimfuno ezinjengomthetho".
I-North Korea ithembise kwintlanganiso ne-Moon kule nyanga ukuba iza kuwucima umzi wayo wokwakha izixhobo zenyukliya ukuba i-United States ithatha "amanyathelo afanayo".
Wathi uKim wamxelela ukuba "iindlela ezihambelanayo" ebezifuna ziigaranti zokhuseleko uTrump azibophelele eSingapore kunye nokuhamba ngendlela eqhelekileyo yolwalamano neWashington.
Abafundi baseHarvard bafunda indlela yokuphumla ngokwaneleyo
Ikhosi entsha kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard kulo nyaka iye yabangela ukuba bonke abafundi bayo bafumane ixesha elingakumbi lokulala ukuze balwe nenkcubeko ekhulayo yokufunda ngokufunda ubusuku bonke ngokutya i-caffeine.
Abafundi abafunda kwiyunivesithi ephambili ehlabathini badla ngokungazi nto xa kufikelelwa kwizinto ezisisiseko ngendlela yokuzinyamekela.
UCharles Czeisler, ongunjingalwazi wezamayeza okulala kwiHarvard Medical School nonguchwepheshe kwiBrigham and Women's Hospital, wayila le khosi, ekholelwa ukuba yeyokuqala ngohlobo lwayo eUnited States.
Waqalisa ukufunda emva kokuba enikele intetho ethetha ngemiphumo yokungalali kakuhle ekufundeni.
'Ekupheleni kwayo enye intombazana yeza kum yaza yathi: 'Kutheni ndixelelwa oku ngoku, kunyaka wam wokugqibela?'
Wathi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ngokubaluleka kokulala - nto leyo eyandimangalisa,' utsho uThe Telegraph.
Le khosi, eye yasasazwa okokuqala kulo nyaka, ichaza indlela imikhwa emihle yokulala enokunceda ngayo abafundi bafunde kakuhle baze babe zizityebi, ibe inokuphucula impilo yabo.
UPowul Barreira, ongunjingalwazi wezifo zengqondo kwiHarvard Medical School nomlawuli weenkonzo zempilo eyunivesithi, wathi iyunivesithi yagqiba ekubeni iqalise le khosi emva kokufumanisa ukuba abafundi balele nzima phakathi evekini.
Le khosi ithatha iyure iquka uthotho lwemisebenzi enxibelelanayo.
Kwelinye icandelo kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokulala, apho abafundi bacofa iikomityi zekofu, amakhethini, iiseti zokuqeqesha kunye neencwadi ukuze baxelelwe ngemiphumo yecaffeine nokukhanya nendlela ukusebenza kwezemidlalo okuchaphazeleka ngayo kukungalali ngokwaneleyo, nokubaluleka kokuhamba ngexesha lokulala.
Kwelinye icandelo, abantu ababandakanyekayo baxelelwa ngendlela ukungalali ngokwaneleyo okunokunyusa ngayo umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa sisifo sentliziyo, ukubetha isisu, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Umfanekiso wendawo ekukho kuyo ikhampasi, onemifanekiso enemifanekiso, ukhuthaza abo banenxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngezinto abazenzayo mihla le.
'Siyazi ukuba akuyi kutshintsha indlela abaziphatha ngayo abafundi ngoko nangoko.
Kodwa sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokwazi - kanye njengokuba nawe unelungelo lokwazi iingozi zempilo zokutshaya", wongezelela ngelitshoyo uProf Czeisler.
Uthe inkcubeko yokuzingca 'ngokuchitha ubusuku bonke' isekhona, esongezelela ngelithi ubugcisa bale mihla kunye noxinzelelo oluthe chatha kubafundi luye lwabangela ukuba ukungalali kube yingxaki ekhulayo.
Ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulala ngokwaneleyo, ubuthongo obuhle, kufanele kube 'sisikhali' somfundi sokulwa uxinezeleko, ukudinwa kunye noxinezeleko, utshilo - nokuba ukuphepha ukwanda emzimbeni, njengoko ukulala kubeka ingqondo kwimeko yokulamba, ibenza bahlale belambile.
URaymond So, umfana waseCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala ofunda ikhemistri nobomi, wancedisa uNjingalwazi Czeisler ekuqulunqeni le khosi, ekubeni wayethathe enye yeeklasi zakhe kunyaka ophelileyo ebudeni bonyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
Wathi le khosi yamenza waqonda ukuba kufuneka kubekho izifundo eziza kufundiswa bonke abafundi.
Uthe inyathelo elilandelayo, kukuba bonke abafundi abaphumelele kwizifundo zobugqirha bafune ukugqiba inkqubo efana nale ngaphambi kokuba bangenele iziko eliphembelela ukhuphiswano.
