UKanye West Uqalise Ukuxolisa KuTrump, Enxibe Isigqoko se-MAGA, Emva kokuBonakala kwakhe kwi-SNL.
Izinto Azenzanga Ngcono
UKanye West wabhokiswa kakhulu kwi-studio ngexesha lomdlalo we-Saturday Night Live emva kokudlala ngendlela engaqondakaliyo apho wayedumisa uMongameli wase-US uDonald Trump waza wathi uza kubaleka kwithuba lika-2020.
Emva kokwenza ingoma yakhe yesithathu ngobo busuku, ebizwa ngokuba yiGhost Town apho wayenxibe i-Make America Great cap, waqhubeka nokugxeka amaDemocrats kwaye waphinda wamxhasa uTrump.
"Kaninzi ndithetha nomntu omhlophe athi: "Ungamthanda njani uTrump, ungumntu okhetha uhlanga?"
Ukuba bendinalo ixhala ngobuhlanga, bendinokufuduka eMelika kudala", utshilo.
I-SNL iqale ngomboniso weqonga eliphambili likaMatt Damon apho inkwenkwezi yaseHollywood yakwenza intlekisa ubungqina bukaBrett Kavanaugh phambi kweKomiti yezoBulungisa yeBhunga leSenate kwizityholo zokuhlaselwa ngokwesondo ezenziwe nguChristine Blasey Ford.
Nangona ingasasazwanga, umfanekiso kaWest wesithuko walayishwa kwi-media media ngumculi uChris Rock.
Akucaci ukuba uRok wayezama ukuhlekisa ngoWest ngokumthumela.
Kwakhona, uWest wayekhalaze kubaphulaphuli esithi uye wafumana ixesha elinzima emva kweqonga ngenxa yokunxiba kwakhe intloko.
"Bandiphoxa emva kweqonga.
Bathi, 'musa ukuphuma phaya unaloo mbasa.'
Bandixhaphaza!
Bathi ke mna ndikwindawo etshone phantsi", watsho njalo, ngokutsho kweWashington Examiner.
UWest waqhubeka: "Ngaba ufuna ukubona indawo etshona?" esithi wayeza "kufaka ikeyiki yam yesuperman, kuba oku kuthetha ukuba awukwazi ukundixelela ukuba ndenze ntoni.
Zama uthando".
Iimbono zakhe zabangela ukuba abaphulaphuli babhengeze kabini yaye amalungu eqela leSNL abonakala eneentloni, iVariety yanikela ingxelo, omnye umntu apho exelela eli phephancwadi: "Iqela lonke lahlala cwaka".
UWest wayeqeshwe njengendawo engekhoyo kwicala leemvumi uAriana Grande, owayesakuba ngumtshakazi wakhe, irapper uMac Miller, owafayo kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo.
UWest wabhida abaninzi ngokwenza ingoma ethi I Love it, enxibe njengePerrier Bottle.
UWest wafumana inkxaso kumongameli weqela elingumgcini-sixhelo iTPUSA, uCandace Turner owatyhila kwi-Twitter wathi: "Kwenye yezona mphefumlo zinesibindi: NDITHATHA KUNYE NJENGOKO WENZA UKUZIMA KWIINTSHOLONGANE".
Kodwa umninimzi wethokhwe uKaren Hunter wathetha ngelithi uWest "ubonakalisa ubuntu bakhe yaye oko kumangalisa ngokwenene".
"Kodwa ndakhetha UKUSABONGA umntu (ngokuthenga umculo okanye impahla yakhe okanye ukuxhasa "ubugcisa" bakhe) endikholwa ukuba wamkela yaye ukhupha ingcamango eyingozi kuluntu lwam.
Ukhululekile.
Nathi kunjalo", wongeze watsho.
Ngaphambi kokuba le ngoma ibonwe, lo mculi wabhengeza kwi-Twitter ukuba utshintshe igama lakhe, esithi ngoku "uyaziwa ngokusemthethweni njengoKanye West".
Akanguye umculi wokuqala ukutshintsha igama lakhe kwaye ulandela emanyathelweni kaDiddy, okwabizwa ngokuba nguPuff Daddy, Puffy noP Diddy.
Umculi we-rap, uSnoop Dogg, wabizwa ngokuba nguSnoop Lion yaye ngokuqinisekileyo umculi owayeswelekile, uPrince, watshintsha igama lakhe waba ngumfuziselo waza ke umculi owayesaziwa ngokuba nguPrince.
