Inkwenkwezi yeGame of Thrones uKit Harington uhlasela ubudoda obunetyhefu
UKit Harington waziwa ngokuba ngumdlali odlala indima kaJon Snow kumdlalo weHBO wefantasy we Game of Thrones.
Kodwa lo mdlali weqonga, oneminyaka engama-31 ubudala, uye wabetha kwizithethe zeqhawe elingumntu onamandla, esithi iindima ezinjalo ezikwizikrini zenza amakhwenkwe aselula avakalelwe kukuba kufuneka abe ngqwabalala ukuze ahlonitshwe.
Ethetha neThe Sunday Times Culture, uKit wathi ukholelwa ukuba 'kukho into engalunganga' yaye wabuza ukuba angalusingatha njani na ingxaki yobudoda obunetyhefu kwixesha lika #MeToo.
UKit, osandul' ukutshata noRose Leslie, naye oneminyaka engama-31 ubudala, naye owayedlala kwiGame of Thrones, wavuma ukuba 'unomdla' wokujongana nale ngxaki.
'Ndivakalelwa kukuba, ngokuqinisekileyo, ngoku - siye saphambuka phi ngobudoda?,' watsho.
'Siye sabafundisa ntoni abantu besakhula, xa sijonga ingxaki esiyibona ngoku?'
UKit ukholelwa ukuba umabonwakude usenokuba ngoyena nobangela wokwanda kobudoda obuyingozi ngenxa yokuba unabalingiswa abakhuthaza ubudoda.
Waqhubeka esithi: 'Yintoni esendalo yaye yintoni efundiswayo?
Yintoni efundiswayo kumabonwakude, nasezitratweni, eyenza amakhwenkwe aselula avakalelwe kukuba afanele abe yile nkalo ethile yokuba yindoda?
Ndicinga ukuba lowo ngomnye wemibuzo ebalulekileyo kweli xesha lethu - singakutshintsha njani oko?
Kuba ngokucacileyo kukho into engahambanga kakuhle kubafana abaselula.'
Kule ncoko wavuma ukuba akasayi kwenza nayiphi na i-Game of Thrones prequels okanye iziqendu xa uthotho luphela ehlotyeni elizayo, esithi 'wenziwe ngamabala emfazwe kunye namahashe'.
Ukususela ngoNovemba uKit uza kudlala kwifilimu kaSam Shepard ethi True West, ibali lomvelisi wefilimu nomntakwabo, ongumphangi.
Lo mdlali weqonga kutshanje utyhile ukuba ukudibana nomfazi wakhe uRose ukujonga njengona nto ilungileyo evela kwiGame of Thrones.
Wathi: 'Ndidibene nomfazi wam kulo mboniso, ngoko ngaloo ndlela wandinika intsapho yam yexesha elizayo, nobomi bam ukususela ngoku kuse phambili.'
URose wadlala indima kaYgritte, umdla wothando lomlingisi kaKit uJon Snow, kuthotho lwefantasy oluphumelele i-Emmy.
Esi sibini satshata ngoJuni 2018 kwintsimi yendlu kaLeslie eScotland.
I-HIV/AIDS: I-China ibika ukwanda ngama-14% kwiimeko ezintsha
I-China iye yabhengeza ukuba inani labemi bayo abanentsholongwane kaGawulayo nesifo sikaGawulayo liye lantinga nge-14%
Amagosa ezempilo athi, bangaphezu kwama-820 000 abantu abachaphazelekayo kweli lizwe.
Kwikota yesibini yonyaka ka-2018 kuphela, kuye kwakho abantu abatsha abamalunga nama-40 000 abanesifo sikaGauteng.
Uninzi lwezifo ezitsha lwalusasazeka ngesondo, nto leyo eyayibonisa ukuba izinto zitshintshile.
Ngokwesithethe, iHIV isasazeka ngokukhawuleza kwezinye iindawo zaseTshayina ngenxa yokutofelwa igazi elosulelekileyo.
Kodwa inani labantu abanentsholongwane kaGawulayo ngale ndlela liye lancitshiswa laya kutsho phantse ku - zero, ngokutsho kweziphathamandla zempilo zaseTshayina kwinkomfa eyayikwiphondo laseYunnan.
Noko ke, nyaka ngamnye inani labantu abaneHIV noGawulayo eTshayina liye landa ngabantu abali - 100 000.
Ukudluliselwa kweHIV ngesini yingxaki enkulu kuluntu lwaseTshayina lwe-LGBT.
Ngowe-1997 ubufanasini babungekho mthethweni eTshayina, kodwa ucalucalulo kubantu abangama-LGBT kuthiwa lugqugqisile.
Ngenxa yemilinganiselo engqongqo yelizwe, uhlolisiso luye lwabonisa ukuba amadoda angama-70 ukuya kuma-90% alala namadoda ekugqibeleni aya kutshata namabhinqa.
Uninzi lwezifo ezosulelayo luvela kukungakhuselwa ngokwaneleyo kwezesini kwezi ngxuba.
Ukususela ngowama-2003, urhulumente waseTshayina uye wathembisa ukuba wonke umntu uza kufumana amayeza okuxhathisa intsholongwane kaGawulayo ukuze kulawulwe le ngxaki.
