NgoMgqibelo, uMaxine Waters waseUnited States wagxeka izityholo zokuba ilungu labasebenzi bakhe liye lafaka inkcazelo yobuqu yamalungu amathathu e-Republican US Senators kumaphepha omthetho e-Wikipedia.
