Ingxelo eyavela kwi-intanethi ngoLwesine, yabhalwa ngumntu ongaziwayo kwiCapitol Hill ngexesha lokuxoxwa kwetyala lokuziphatha kakubi ngokwesondo elichotshelwe uMongameli weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh.
