IsiNgesi kunye neBough baqala i-odyssey yabo ye-high-jink: bazimele njengabalindi, batshisa indawo yokutyela yaseFransi; benza ingozi ngokuthumela ngokwabo kwi-yacht kaVolta; kwaye isiNgesi sibangela ukungabikho komthetho njengoko ezama ukusebenzisa i-headset ye-Virtual Reality ukuze aziqhelanise necala langaphakathi lendlu kaVolta.
