Yintoni I-Global Citizen Festival yaye Ngaba Yenze Nantoni Na Ukunciphisa Ubuhlwempu?
NgoMgqibelo, eNew York kuza kubakho uMnyhadala Wabantu Bezizwe Ngezizwe, umsitho womculo owenziwa minyaka le onoludwe lweenkwenkwezi ezibalaseleyo eziza kudlala kunye nomsebenzi omhle ngokulinganayo; ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ehlabathini.
Ngoku, emva kweminyaka esixhenxe, iGlobal Citizen Festival iza kubona amawaka-waka abantu esiya kwiGreat Lawn yaseCentral Park ukuze banganeli nje ukunandipha abantu abanjengoJanet Jackson, uCardi B noShawn Mendes, kodwa kwakhona ukuze baqwalasele injongo yokwenene yalo mbhiyozo yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu obunganyamezelekiyo ngowama-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival, eyabhengezwa ngo-2012, yongezwa yi-Global Poverty Project, iqela elixhasa amazwe ngamazwe elindele ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ngokunyusa inani labantu abalwa nalo.
Ukuze bafumane itikiti elihlawulelwayo kumsitho (ngaphandle kokuba bebenokuhlawula itikiti elihlawulelwa abantu abakhethekileyo), abantu ababeza kuqhuba le nkonzo kwakufuneka benze uthotho lwemisebenzi, okanye "izenzo" ezifana nokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyili kwinkokeli yehlabathi, ukufowuna okanye ezinye iindlela ezinentsingiselo zokunceda abantu bazi injongo yabo yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
Kodwa iGlobal Citizen iye yaphumelela kangakanani xa kusele iminyaka eli-12 ukuze iphumelele?
Ngaba ukuvuza abantu ngomboniso wamahhala yindlela yokwenene yokweyisela abantu ukuba bafune isibhengezo sokwenza okuthile, okanye ngaba yenye nje imeko yento ebizwa ngokuba yi "clicktivism" - abantu abavakalelwa kukuba benza umahluko wokwenene ngokusayina isicelo esikwi-intanethi okanye ngokuthumela i-tweet?
Ukususela ngowama-2011, iGlobal Citizen ithi iye yafumana "izenzo" ezingaphezu kwezigidi ezili-19 ezivela kubaxhasi bayo, befuna ukuphumeza usukelo olwahlukileyo.
Ithi ezi zenzo ziye zanceda iinkokeli zehlabathi ukuba zichaze izibophelelo nemigaqo-nkqubo elingana namawaka ezigidi ezingama-R37 ezaziza kuchaphazela ubomi babantu abangaphezu kwamawaka ezigidi ezingama-2,5 ngowama-2030.
Ekuqaleni konyaka ka-2018, eli qela lathi liye lazibophelela kwaye labhengeza izivumelwano ezingama-390 ezibangelwa zizenzo zalo, ubuncinane i-$10 billion yazo sele ihlawulwe okanye ifunyenwe.
Eli qela liqikelela ukuba ukuza kuthi ga ngoku ezi mali ziqinisekisiweyo ziye zaba nefuthe ngokuthe ngqo kubantu abamalunga nezigidi ezingama-649 ehlabathini lonke.
Ezinye zezinto eziphambili eziza kuqinisekiswa ziquka iThe Power of Nutrition, intsebenziswano yase-UK yabatyali mali nabaphumezi bemigudu abazimisele "ukunceda abantwana bakhule bafikelele kumandla abo", ethembisa ukunika iRwanda i$35 yezigidi ukunceda ukuphelisa ukungondleki kweli lizwe emva kokufumana i-tweets ezingaphezu kwe-4 700 ezivela kwiiGlobal Citizens.
"Ngokuxhaswa ngurhulumente wase-UK, abanikeli, oorhulumente belizwe, kunye nabemi behlabathi njengawe, singenza ukungabikho kokusesikweni kwezentlalo kokungondlekiyo kube ngumzekelo kwimbali", uthethe watsho uTracey Ullman, ongummeli weThe Power of Nutrition, kwisihlwele ngexesha lekhonsathi ephilayo eLondon ngoAprili 2018.
Eli qela likwathi emva kokuba kwenziwe amalungiselelo angaphezu kwama-5 000 okucela i-U.K. ukuba iphucule indlela yokondla oomama nabantwana, urhulumente wabhengeza ukuba uza kuxhasa ngezimali iprojekthi, iPower of Nutrition, eza kunceda abantu abangama-5 ezigidi ababhinqileyo nabantwana ngokutya.
Xa uphendula omnye wemibuzo ebuzwa rhoqo kwiwebhsayithi yayo ebuza "Yintoni ekwenza ucinge ukuba sinokuphelisa ubuhlwempu obugqithiseleyo?"
