Kodwa, njengamaqela amakhulu amalungelo oluntu nawokuchasa ucalu-calulo ngaphambi kwethu, siya kuphumelela, kuba xa sisonke sisemagqabini.
UJanet Jackson, uWeeknd, uShawn Mendes, uCardi B, uJanelle Monáe baphakathi kweminye yemisebenzi ezakubakho kulo msitho wonyaka eNew York, eza kube iqhutywa nguDeborra-Lee Furness noHugh Jackman.
