"Kuba nzima gqitha", watsho umama oneminyaka engama-35 ubudala uRisa Kusuma, xa wayethuthuzela usana lwakhe olunefebhu kwiziko labantu abafudukela kwisixeko sasePalu.
"Mzuzu ngamnye iambulensi izisa imizimba.
Amanzi acocekileyo anqabile".
Abantu ababehlala apho babonakala bebuyela kumakhaya abo atshabalalisayo, behl' amahlongwane kwizinto zabo ezimanzi, bezama ukuhlangula nantoni na ababenokuyifumana.
Kwakukho amakhulu abantu abenzakeleyo yaye izibhedlele ezazonakaliswe yinyikima enkulu, zazonganyelwe.
Abanye abalimalayo, kuquka uDwi Haris, owaphuka umqolo nehlombe, babephumle ngaphandle kwesibhedlele sasePalu, apho izigulana bezinyanyekelwa ngaphandle ngenxa yenyikima eqhubekayo.
Iinyembezi zazehlela emehlweni akhe njengoko wayebalisa indlela eyadudulwa ngayo yinyikima eyayinamandla kwigumbi lakhe lokulala kwihotele elikumgangatho wesihlanu awayehlala kulo nomfazi wakhe nentombi yakhe.
"Asisayi kuba nalo ixesha lokuzikhusela.
Ndicinga ukuba ndadibana namabhodlo alo donga", watsho uHaris kwiAssociated Press, esongezelela ngelithi intsapho yakhe yayisezidolophini ukuze iye kumsitho womtshato.
"Ndava umfazi wam ekhalela uncedo, kodwa emva koko kwathi cwaka.
Andazi ukuba kwenzeka ntoni kuye nakumntwana wam.
Ndiyathemba ukuba bakhuselekile".
U-Ambassador wase-US utyhola i-China 'ngokuxhaphaza' ngeentengiso 'zokuqhwayela'
Kwiveki emva kokuba iphephandaba laseTshayina lipapashe iphephandaba laseUnited States elinamaphepha amane lichaza ngeengenelo zokurhweba phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina, ummeli waseUnited States eChina wamtyhola uPekong ngokusebenzisa amajelo aseUnited States ukusasaza ubuxoki.
UMongameli waseMerika uDonald Trump ngoLwesithathu odlulileyo uye wathetha nge-China Daily kwiDes Moines Register - iphephandaba elithengisa kakhulu laseIowa - emva kokutyhola iChina ngokufuna ukuphazamisa ukhetho lwe-US Congress ngoNovemba 6, ityala eliphikiswa yiChina.
Isityholo sikaTrump sokuba iPeking izama ukuphazamisana kunyulo lwaseMerika siphawulile oko amagosa aseMerika akuxelela iReuters kwakuyinqanaba elitsha kwiphulo elandayo laseWashington lokubeka uxinzelelo eChina.
Ngoxa kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe babeke iintengiso zokukhuthaza urhwebo, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zibanjwe kwimfazwe yorhwebo eyondeleleneyo eye yababona behlabela mgama ngokurhafisa amaxabiso kwiimveliso zomnye nomnye.
Iingcali zaseTshayina nezaseMerika zithi, intlawulo yaseTshayina ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo yayenzelwe ukubetha abathengisi bamazwe afana neIowa abaxhasa iRepublican Party kaTrump.
UTerry Branstad, usithunywa saseMelika eChina nowayesakuba ngumphathi weIowa, ummeli omkhulu wezinto zezolimo eziya eChina, wathi iPeking yenzakalise abasebenzi baseMelika, amafama namashishini.
IChina, uBranstad wabhala kwicandelo lezimvo kwiDes Moines Register yangeCawa, "ngoku iphindaphinda loo nto yokuxhaphaza ngokuhambisa iintengiso zentengiso kumaphephandaba ethu akhululekileyo".
UBranstad wabhala wathi: "Ngokusasaza intetho ephosakeleyo, urhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa isithethe saseMerika sokuthetha ngokukhululekileyo nokukhulula amajelo eendaba ngokubeka intengiso ehlawulwayo kwiDes Moines Register".
"Ngokwahlukileyo koko, kwivenkile yephephandaba ezantsi apha eBeijing, uya kufumana amazwi ambalwa avuselelayo yaye akuyi kubakho nto ibonisa ukuba abantu baseTshayina banezimvo ezahlukileyo ngeengxaki zezoqoqosho, ekubeni abeendaba belawulwa ngamandla liQela lamaKomanisi", ubhala njalo.
Wongezelela ngelithi "elinye lamaphephandaba aziwayo aseTshayina alizange lifune ukupapasha" inqaku lakhe, nangona engazange alichaze ukuba liliphi iphephandaba.
AbaPolitiki Bawaphambukisayo Abavoti Abafazi Phambi KweeMidterm Ngeentlekele zikaKavanaugh, Abahlalutyi Balumkisa
Njengoko amaRiphabliki amaninzi aphambili ekhusela umgqatswa weNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh kwizityholo eziliqela zokuhlaselwa ngokwesini, abahlalutyi baye balumkisa ngelithi baya kubona impikiswano, ingakumbi evela kubafazi, ngexesha lonyulo oluzayo lwaphakathi kwexesha.
Iimvakalelo ezijikeleze oku bezingaphezulu kakhulu, yaye uninzi lweeRiphabliki sele lubonise ukuba zifuna ukuqhubeka nokuvota.
Ezi zinto azinakuphinda zenziwe", utshilo uGrant Reeher, unjingalwazi kwicandelo lezepolitiki kwiSikolo iMaxwell kwiYunivesithi yaseSyracuse kwiThe Hill kwinqaku elipapashwe ngoMgqibelo.
UReeher uthe uthandabuza ukuba umzuzu wokugqibela kaSenator Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) wokunyusa uphando lwe-FBI uya kwanela ukuzoyisa abavoti abanomsindo.
"Abafazi abayi kukulibala oko kwenzekayo izolo - abayi kukulibala ngomso yaye abayi kukulibala ngoNovemba", watsho uKarin Jean-Pierre, umcebisi oyintloko nongumthetheli wesizwe weqela elihambela phambili i-MoveOn ngoLwesihlanu, ngokutsho kwephephandaba laseWashington, D.C.
Ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, abaqhankqalazi babetha umkhosi besithi "Nyaka omtsha uyeza!" njengoko babeqhankqalaza kwiholo yeNdlu yeeNgwevu njengoko amaRiphabhlikhi alawula iKomiti yezoBulungisa akhetha ukuqhubela phambili ukonyulwa kukaKavanaugh nangona ubungqina bukaGqirha Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ingxelo.
UStu Rothenberg, umhlalutyi wezobupolitika ongekho mthethweni, uxelele le webhsayithi yeendaba esithi: "Uzinzo nentshukumisa yedemokhrasi ziza kuba yinto engaqhelekanga".
"Abantu bathi sele liphezulu; oko kuyinyaniso.
Kodwa isenokuba ngaphezulu, ngokukodwa phakathi kwabafazi abavota kwiindawo ezisemaphandleni naphakathi kwabavoti abaselula, abaneminyaka eli-18 ukuya kwengama-29 ubudala, abathi nangona bengamthandi umongameli, ngokufuthi bangavoti".
Nangaphambi kokuba uFord anikele ubungqina esidlangalaleni echaza ngeenkcukacha zakhe zokubekwa kweliso ngokwesondo kumgqatswa weNkundla ePhakamileyo, abahlalutyi bacebisa ukuba kungabakho impindezelo ukuba amaRiphabliki ayaqhubeka nokungqinisisa.
Ngokutsho kwe-NBC News, ekuqaleni kweveki ephelileyo uMichael Steele, owayesakuba ngusihlalo weKomiti yeSizwe yamaRiphabhlikhi, wathi: "Le nto iye yaba yingxaki enkulu kwiGOP".
"Ayisosigqibo sokuba ikomiti iya kuvuma okanye ivoto yokugqibela okanye ukuba uKavanaugh uyabekwa na ebhentshini, kodwa kukwabhekiswa kwindlela amaRiphabliki akuphethe ngayo oku nendlela aye amphatha ngayo", uGuy Cecil, umlawuli we-Priorities USA, iqela elinceda amaDemocrats, wacacisa oko kwijelo leendaba.
Noko ke, kubonakala ngathi abantu baseMerika abavumelani ukuba ngubani abamele bamthembe emva kokungqinwa kukaFord noKavanaugh, yaye bakhetha icala lesibini.
Uhlolisiso olutsha olwenziwa yi-YouGov lubonisa ukuba ama-41% abo bafunyenweyo ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi babukholelwa ubungqina bukaFord, ngoxa ama-35% athi ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi babukholelwa ubungqina bukaKavanaugh.
Ukongezelela, ama-38% athi acinga ukuba uKavanaugh mhlawumbi okanye ngokuqinisekileyo waxoka ngexesha lobungqina bakhe, ngoxa kuphela ngama-30% athi okufanayo ngoFord.
IThe Guardian yathi, emva kokutyhefwa nguFlake, iFBI ngoku iphengulula izityholo eziziswe nguFord kunye nesinye isimangalo, uDeborah Ramirez.
UFord uye wangqina phambi kweKomiti yezoBulungisa yeNdlu yeeNgwevu phantsi kwesifungo kwiveki ephelileyo ukuba uKavanaugh wamhlasela enxilile xa wayeneminyaka eli-17 ubudala.
URamirez uthi umnyulwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo wamtyhila amalungu akhe okuzala ngoxa babekwiqela ebudeni bexesha labo lokufunda eYale ngeminyaka yee-1980.
Umyili WeWebhu Yehlabathi Lonke Uceba Ukuqalisa I-Internet Entsha Ukuze Ajamelane NoGoogle NoFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, umyili weWebhu Ebanzi Yehlabathi, uqalisa ishishini elitsha elifuna ukukhuphisana neFacebook, iAmazon neGoogle.
Iprojekthi yakutshanje yale ngcali yeteknoloji, i-Inrupt, yinkampani eyakha phezu kweplatfom yomthombo ovulekileyo kaBerners-Lee i-Solid.
I-Solid ivumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe apho kugcinwa khona idatha yabo kwaye ngabantu abavumelekayo ukuba bafikelele kulwazi.
Kudliwano-ndlebe olukhethekileyo neFast Company, uBerners-Lee waqhekeza esithi injongo yeInrupt "kukulawula ihlabathi".
Wathi: "Kufuneka sikwenze ngoku", ethetha ngokuqalisa kwethu.
"Yinto yembali".
Le app isebenzisa iteknoloji yeSolid ukuvumela abantu ukuba bazenzele "indawo yabo yokugcina idatha ekwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Inokuqulatha uluhlu lwabafowunelwa, uluhlu lwezinto ekufuneka zenziwe, ikhalenda, ithala leencwadi lomculo nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezobuchule.
Kufana neGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify zonke ziyafumaneka kwi-browser enye ngaxeshanye.
Into ekhethekileyo ngevenkile yedatha yobuqu ekwi-intanethi kukuba kuxhomekeke ngokupheleleyo kumsebenzisi ukuba ngubani onokufikelela koluphi uhlobo lolwazi.
Le nkampani iyibiza ngokuba "kukwenza umntu abe namandla ngenxa yeenkcukacha".
Ingcamango ye-Inrupt, ngokutsho kwe-CEO yenkampani uJohn Bruce, kukuba inkampani izise izixhobo, iinkqubo kunye nezakhono ezifanelekileyo zokuncedisa ukwenza i-Solid ifumaneke kumntu wonke.
Le nkampani ngoku iquka uBerners-Lee, uBruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elithengwe yi-IBM, abanye abasebenzi abaphuhlisi abaqeshwe ukuba basebenze kwiprojekthi, kunye noluntu lwabasebenzisi beekhowudi.
Ukususela kule veki, abaphuhlisi bezinto zobugcisa ehlabathini lonke banokuzenzela ezabo iiapps ezisemthethweni besebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhsayithi yeInrupt.
UBerners-Lee wathi yena neqela lakhe abathethi "noFacebook noGoogle malunga nokuba bangatshintsha ngokupheleleyo na okanye bangatshintshi apho zonke iimodeli zabo zoshishino zitshintshwe ngokupheleleyo ngobusuku obunye.
"Asizukucela imvume kubo".
Kwiphepha elibhalwe ngoMgqibelo, uBerners-Lee wabhala wathi umsebenzi weInrupt "kukubonelela ngombane wentengiso kunye nenkqubo yendalo ukunceda ukukhusela ingqibelelo nomgangatho womnatha omtsha owakhiwe kwiSolid".
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee wayiguqula i-Internet xa waseka iWorld Wide Web Consortium kwiMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee uye waba lizwi elinempembelelo kwingxoxo yokungathathi cala komnatha.
Nangona esungula i-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuhlala enguMsunguli noMlawuli weWorld Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation kunye neZiko leDatha evulekileyo.
"Ndiyavuya gqitha ngenxa yale mihla yewebhu", wongezelela ngelitshoyo uBerners-Lee.
UBernard Vann: WW1 Victoria Cross umfundisi obhiyozelwayo
Kwiminyaka eli-100 edluleyo, kwidolophu yakowabo kuye kwaqhutywa umbhiyozo wembeko yendoda ekukuphela kwayo eyayingumfundisi weCawa yaseNgilani eyafumana umnqamlezo kaVictoria ebudeni beMfazwe Yehlabathi Yokuqala njengomlwi.
ULt Col Umfundisi Bernard Vann wafumana ibhaso ngomhla wama 29 kweyoKwindla ngo 1918 ekuhlaseleni eBellenglise naseLehaucourt.
Noko ke, wabulawa ngumbulali obulala ngogqo-ngqesho kwiintsuku ezine kamva yaye akazange afumanise ukuba wayefumene eyona mbeko iphakamileyo yasemkhosini yaseBritani.
Ilitye lesikhumbuzo latyhilwa ngoomzukulwana bakhe ababini kumngcelele owawuseRushden, eNorthamptonshire, ngoMgqibelo.
Omnye wabazukulwana bakhe, uMichael Vann, wathi "ngokucacileyo" ilitye laliza kutyhilwa kwiminyaka eli-100 emva kokuphumelela koyisemkhulu.
Ngokwe London Gazette, ngomhla ka 29 Septemba 1918 uLt Col Vann wakhokela ibutho lakhe kwi Canal de Saint-Quentin "ngenkungu etyebileyo kakhulu nangaphantsi komlilo onzima ovela kumhlaba nakumatshini".
Kamva wakhawuleza waya kumgca wokudubula kwaye "ngobungqina obukhulu" wakhokela umgca ngaphambi kokugxotha umpu wentsimi ngesandla esinye kwaye wakhupha abathathu kwiqela.
ULt Col Vann wabulawa ngumtshutshisi waseJamani ngowama-4 Oktobha 1918 - kwisithuba esingaphezu kwenyanga ngaphambi kokuba imfazwe iphele.
UMichael Vann, oneminyaka engama-72 ubudala, wathi izenzo zikayisemkhulu "yinto endiyaziyo ukuba andinakuze ndiyifikelele kodwa yinto ebonakalisa ukuthobeka".
Yena nomntakwabo uGqr James Vann bafaka umququ emva komngcelele, owawukhokelwa yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
UMichael Vann uthe "uziva enembeko kakhulu ukuba nenxaxheba kulo mbhiyozo" wongezelela ngelithi "ubungqina beqhawe lokwenene buboniswa yinkxaso eza kunikwa ngabantu abaninzi".
Abalandeli beMMA bahlala ubusuku bonke bebukele iBellator 206, bona bafumana iPeppa Pig endaweni yoko
Khawube nomfanekiso-ngqondweni woku, uye wahlala uphapheme ubusuku bonke ukuze ubukele iBelator 206 ezele phaya kuphela ukuze uthintelwe ukubukela umsitho oyintloko.
Le ngqungquthela yaseSan Jose yayineembambano ezili-13, kuquka nezintandathu kwicandelo eliphambili kwaye yayiboniswe ngqo ebusuku kwi-UK kwiChannel 5.
Ngentsimbi yesi-6 kusasa, kanye xa uGegard Mousasi noRory MacDonald babelungiselela ukujongana, ababukeli base-UK bashiyeka bemangalisiwe xa ingxelo yatshintshela kuPeppa Pig.
Abanye abazange bachukumiseke emva kokuba belele de kwasekuseni ingakumbi ngenxa yokulwa.
Omnye umlandeli kwi-Twitter wachaza ukutshintshela kwi-cartoon yabantwana "njengohlobo oluthile lwehlazo elibi".
"Kungummiselo karhulumente ukuba ngentsimbi yesi-6 kusasa loo mxholo wawungalungelelekanga ngoko kwafuneka batshintshele kwinkqubo yabantwana, " utshilo uDave Schwartz, usekela mongameli ophezulu wezentengiso nonxibelelwano kwiBellator, xa ebuzwa ngolu tshintsho.
"Peppa ihagu", ewe.
Umongameli wenkampani iBellator uScott Coker uthe baza kusebenza kwishedyuli yabo ukuze babandakanye ababukeli base-UK kwixesha elizayo.
"Ndicinga ukuba xa ndicinga ngokudlala kwakhona, ndicinga ukuba sinokuyisingatha le nto", watsho njalo uCoker.
"Kodwa kusekuseni ngeCawa apho yaye asiyi kukwazi ukuyicombulula le nto de kube ngeCawa ngexesha lethu, ngoMvulo ngexesha labo.
Kodwa sisebenza kuyo.
Ndikholelwe, xa yayitshintshile kwakukho imiyalezo emininzi eyayidluliselwa yaye yayingenabubele.
Sasizama ukuyilungisa, sasicinga ukuba ngumonakalo wobugcisa.
Kodwa kwakungenjalo, yayingumbandela karhulumente.
Ndiyakuthembisa ukuba kwixesha elizayo akuyi kwenzeka.
Siza kuyinciphisa ibe yimilo emihlanu endaweni yemithandathu - njengoko siqhele ukwenza - saza sazama ukuzidlulisela kubalandeli saza sawela.
Le yimeko engentle".
I-Desert Island Discs: UTom Daley waziva 'engongasentla' ngokubhekisele kwisini
Umntu ohamba ngokuntywila kwiiOlimpiki uTom Daley uthi wakhula eziva engafaneleki kwabanye ngenxa yesini sakhe - kodwa oko kwamnika inkuthazo yokuba abe yimpumelelo.
Lo mfana uneminyaka engama-24 ubudala wathi akazange aqonde de waya kwisikolo samabanga aphakamileyo ukuba "asinguye wonke ubani ofana nam".
Ethetha kwiRadio 4 Desert Island Discs yokuqala eboniswe nguLauren Laverne, uthe uthethe ngamalungelo ezitabane ukuze anike abanye "ithemba".
Kwakhona wathi ukuba ngumzali kwamenza akanamdla wokuwina kwiiOlimpiki.
Umamkeli oqhelekileyo walo mboniso ohlala ixesha elide, uKirsty Young, uthathe iinyanga eziliqela engekho ngenxa yokugula.
UDaley uthe xa ebonakala njengalowo ungekhoyo kwinkqubo yokuqala kaLaverne, wathi uziva "engaphantsi" kunabanye abantu abakhulayo kuba "bekungamkelekanga ekuhlaleni ukuba uthande amakhwenkwe namantombazana".
Wathi: "Kude kube namhlanje, ezo mvakalelo zokuziva ndingento yanto, nokuziva ndihlukile, ziye zaba zezona zinto ziye zandinika amandla namandla okukwazi ukuphumelela".
Wathi wayefuna ukubonisa ukuba "wayengumntu", ukuze angadanisi mntu xa ekugqibeleni efumanisa ukuba uyathandana.
Lo mdlali weOlimpiki wafumana imbasa yebronze izihlandlo ezibini uye wangummeli ophambili weentlanga zeLGBT yaye uye wenza isibheno ngeentlanga ezininzi ukuba zilungise ubufanasini.
Wathi wayethetha phandle kuba wayeziva enethamsanqa ngokukwazi ukuphila ngaphandle kwemiphumo ibe wayefuna ukunika abanye "ithemba".
Iqhawe lehlabathi izihlandlo ezithathu lathi ukuthandana nendoda - umenzi wefilimu waseUS uDustin Lance Black, awadibana naye ngo-2013 - "kwandibamba ngamanyala".
UDaley utshate nomntu owaphumelela iOscar, oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala kunaye, kunyaka ophelileyo kodwa uthe umsantsa wobudala awuzange ube yingxaki.
Wathi: "Xa ufumana amava amaninzi usemncinci" - waya kwiOlimpiki yakhe yokuqala eneminyaka eli-14 ubudala yaye uyise wabulawa ngumhlaza kwiminyaka emithathu kamva - wathi kwakunzima ukufumana umntu okwiminyaka efanayo naye owafumana amava afana nawe.
Esi sibini saba ngabazali ngoJuni, kunyana ogama linguRobert Ray Black-Daley, kwaye uDaley wathi "imbono yakhe yonke" itshintshile.
"Ukuba ububuze kum kunyaka ophelileyo, bekuya kuba 'kufuneka ndiphumelele imbasa yegolide'", utshilo.
"Kukho izinto ezibaluleke ngakumbi kuneembasa zegolide zeOlimpiki.
Iimbasa zam zegolide zeOlimpiki nguRobbie".
Unyana wakhe unalo igama elifanayo noyise uRobert, owafa ngo-2011 eneminyaka engama-40 emva kokufunyaniswa ukuba unomhlaza wengqondo.
UDaley wathi uyise wayengamamkeli ukuba uza kufa yaye enye yezinto zokugqibela awayibuzayo yayikukuba ingaba babewathathile na amatikiti abo eLondon 2012 - njengoko wayefuna ukuba kumqolo ongaphambili.
Wathi: "Andikwazanga ukumxelela ukuba 'akukho mntu uza kuba ngasemva, utata.'
"Ndandimbambe ngesandla njengoko wayeka ukuphefumla yaye ndade ndakufumanisa ukuba wayesele efile ndaqonda ukuba wayengekho ongenakoyiswa", watsho.
Kunyaka olandelayo uDaley wakhuphisana kwiiOlimpiki zika-2012 waza waphumelela i-bronze.
Wathi: "Ndaqonda ukuba le yinto endandiyiphupha ubomi bam bonke - ukuntywila phambi kwabantu basekuhlaleni kwiMidlalo yeOlimpiki, kwakungekho nto ibhetele kunokuziva ngaloo ndlela".
Kwakhona yaphefumlela ukuba akhethe ingoma yakhe yokuqala - iProud by Heather Small - eyayimenza azive exakekile xa wayelungiselela ukudlala kwiOlimpiki kodwa ke yayisenza abe neentloni.
