Inqanawa entsha yaseJamani yomkhosi wamajoni iye yamiselwa elinye ixesha
Inqanawa entsha yomkhosi wamanzi waseJamani bekufanele ukuba yenziwe ngo-2014 ukuze ithathe indawo yeenqanawa zemfazwe zeMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa ayizukufika kude kube ngunyaka ozayo ngenxa yeenkqubo ezingasebenzi kakuhle kunye neendleko eziphezulu, ingxelo yemithombo yeendaba yendawo.
Ukuthumela "iRheinland-Pfalz", inqanawa ephambili yeBaden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates, ngoku sele ihlehlisiwe ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-2019, ngokutsho kwephephandaba iDie Zeit ecaphula isithethi semikhosi.
Inqanawa ibifanele ukuba ijoyine uMkhosi weNqanawa ngo2014, kodwa iingxaki ezixhalabisayo emva kokuhanjiswa kwaphazamisa isiphelo seprojekthi.
Iinqanawa ezine zeBaden-Wuerttemberg-class eziyalelwe yiNqanawa ngo-2007 ziya kuza endaweni yezikhephe ezidala zeBremen-class.
Kuqondwa ukuba ziza kuba neetoni ezinamandla, uluhlu lwezixhobo zokulwa neenqwelo moya kunye nezixhobo zokulwa neenqanawa kwakunye neendlela ezithile zobugcisa bokusithelisa, ezifana nokunciphisa i-radar, infrared kunye ne-acoustic signatures.
Ezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo zibandakanya ixesha elide lokulondolozwa - kufanele ukuba kwenzeke ukuba kusetyenziswe ezona nqanawa zintsha zintsha kude kube yiminyaka emibini kude nezibuko lasekhaya.
Iphephancwadi iDie Zeit lithi, ukulibaziseka okuqhubekayo kuthetha ukuba iinqanawa zemfazwe eziphucukileyo - ekuthiwa zivumela iJamani ukuba ibe namandla phesheya - ziya kuba zingasasebenzi xa ziqala ukusebenza.
I-F125 eyaba nesiphithiphithi yayisakuba ziindaba zonyaka ophelileyo, xa i-Army yaseJamani yayikwala ngokusemthethweni ukugunyazisa inqanawa yaza yayibuyisela kwi-Blohm & Voss shipyard eHamburg.
Eli yayilixesha lokuqala uMkhosi weenqanawa ubuyisela inqanawa kumakhi wenqanawa emva kokuhanjiswa.
Incinci into eyaziwayo ngezizathu zokubuya, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani athetha ngamanani "esoftware kunye neziphene zehardware" ezenza inqanawa yemfazwe ingasebenzi xa isetyenziswe kumsebenzi wokulwa.
Iintsilelo zesoftware zibaluleke kakhulu kuba iinqanawa zeBaden-Wuerttemberg class ziya kusetyenziswa ngabasebenzi be 120 - kuphela isiqingatha sabasebenzi abakwizikhephe zeBremen class.
Kwakhona, kwavela ukuba inqanawa inzima kakhulu nto leyo enciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye inciphisa amandla oMkhosi weMfazwe ukongeza ukuphuculwa kwexesha elizayo.
Iitoni ezingama-7000 "Rheinland-Pfalz" kukholelwa ukuba inzima ngokuphindwe kabini kunenqanawa ekumgangatho ofanayo osetyenziswe ngamaJamani kwiMfazwe yeHlabathi yesiBini.
Ngaphandle kokungasebenzi kakuhle kwezixhobo zokusebenza, ixabiso elipheleleyo leprojekthi - kuquka nokuqeqeshwa kwabasebenzi - nalo liyingxaki.
Kuthiwa sele ifikelele kwi-€3.1 billion ($3.6 billion) - ukusuka kwi-€2.2 billion.
Iingxaki ezibandakanya i-frigate entsha ziba zibaluleke ngakumbi ekukhanyeni kwezilumkiso zakutshanje ukuba amandla aselwandle aseJamani ayancipha.
Ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, oyintloko yekomiti yokhuselo yasePalamente yaseJamani, wavuma ukuba uMkhosi weenqanawa wenene "uphelelwa ziinqanawa ezinokusetyenziswa".
Igosa lathi lo mba uye wavela ngokuhamba kwexesha, kuba iinqanawa ezindala ziyekisiwe kodwa akukho nqanawa zitshintshiweyo.
Uthe wayixhalabile ukuba akukho namnye kwi-Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates owayekwazi ukujoyina i-Navy.
I-National Trust iphulaphula ubomi obufihlakeleyo bobongqele
Uphando olutsha olwenziwa kwilali yaseScotland Highlands lufuna ukuveza indlela amalulwane awusebenzisa ngayo umhlaba xa efuna ukutya.
Kukho ithemba lokuba oku kuya kunceda ekuchazeni indlela ezi zilwanyana ezizilwanyana ezibaleka ngayo ezi zizodwa yaye kuya kunceda ekuqondiseni imisebenzi yokulondoloza ezi zilwanyana kwixesha elizayo.
Uhlolisiso olwenziwa zizazinzulu kwiNational Trust yaseSkotlani luya kulandela iimpukane eziqhelekileyo nezingxondorha kwakunye neempukane ezindlebe zide ezinsundu neDaubenton kwiGadi yaseInverewe eWester Ross.
Kuya kubekwa izixhobo ezikhethekileyo kwiindawo ezibalulekileyo ezikufutshane ukuze kubekwe umkhondo kwimisebenzi yeengcuka ebudeni bexesha lonyaka.
Abasebenzi be-NHS kunye namavolontiya nabo baya kwenza uphando oluhambayo besebenzisa izixhobo eziphethwe ngesandla.
Ingcali iya kuhlalutya zonke iirekhodi ukuze ibone ukuba zivela kangaphi ezo ngxolo zezilwanyana zasendle nokuba zeziphi iintlobo ezenza ntoni.
Emva koko kuya kwenziwa imephu yendawo yokuhlala kunye nengxelo ukuze kwenziwe umfanekiso opheleleyo wesimo-mhlaba sokuziphatha kwazo.
URob Dewar, umcebisi ngezilwanyana kwiNTS, uthemba ukuba ezi ziphumo ziya kutyhila ukuba yeyiphi eyona ndawo ibalulekileyo kwezi zilwanyana nendlela ezisetyenziswa ngayo.
Olu lwazi luyakunceda ukufumanisa izibonelelo zomsebenzi wolawulo lweendawo zokuhlala ezifana nokudalwa kwamabala kunye nendlela egqwesileyo yokugcina amahlathi kumalulwane nezinye iintlobo ezinxulumene nawo.
Inani leengcongconi eSkotlani naseUnited Kingdom liye lehla kakhulu kule nkulungwane idluleyo.
Zisesichengeni sokwakhiwa nokulungiswa kwezakhiwo ezichaphazela izindlu zokuhlala nokulahleka kwendawo ezihlala kuyo.
Iiphephethi zomoya nezibane nazo zinokuba yingozi, njengokuba kunjalo nangamabhabhathane eempukane nezinye izinto ezisetyenziswayo xa kusakhiwa, kwakunye nokuhlaselwa ziikati.
Iimfene aziboni.
Noko ke, ngenxa yemikhwa yazo yokuzingela ebusuku iindlebe zazo ziluncedo ngakumbi kunamehlo xa kufuneka zibambe ixhoba.
Zisebenzisa ubuchule obuyinkimbinkimbi bokukhangela indawo ezihlala kuyo ukuze ziqonde izitshixo nemiqobo ekuhambeni kwazo.
I-NTS, enoxanduva lokunyamekela izakhiwo zembali ezingaphezu kwama-270, imiyezo ebalulekileyo engama-38 nama-76 000 eehektare zomhlaba kulo lonke eli lizwe, ibamkela ngenyameko ibhabhathane.
Inamagcisa alishumi aqeqeshiweyo, aqhuba rhoqo uphando, ukuhlola indawo yokuhlala kwaye ngamanye amaxesha asindise.
Lo mbutho ude wamisa indawo yokuqala yaseScotland neyokuphela kokulondolozwa kwamatshuntshe kwipropathi yaseThreave eDumfries naseGalloway, nekhaya leentlobo zamashuntshe ezisibhozo kwezilishumi zaseScotland.
Umphathi wepropati uDavid Thompson uthi le ndawo yeyona ifanelekileyo kubo.
Wathi: "Ethreeve le yindawo entle kakhulu yeengwamza.
"Sinezakhiwo ezindala, imithi emininzi ekhulileyo nayo yonke indawo efanelekileyo.
Kodwa kuninzi okusafuneka sikufunde ngamabhabhathane, ngoko umsebenzi esiwenzayo apha nakwezinye iindawo uza kusinceda siqonde ngakumbi ngezinto ezizifunayo ukuze zikhule".
Ugxininisa ukubaluleka kokujonga ukuba azikho na iintshatshu ngaphambi kokuba kulungiswe izakhiwo kuba kunokwenzeka ukuba xa kutshatyalaliswa izindlu zazo, kungatshona amantshontsho angama-400 kunye namantshontsho, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba abantu basekuhlaleni bafe bonke.
Amalulwane akhuselwe kwaye akukho semthethweni ukuwabulala, ukuwahlukumeza okanye ukuwaphazamisa okanye ukutshabalalisa iindawo zawo.
UElisbeth Ferrell, igosa laseScotland leBat Conservation Trust, ukhuthaze uluntu ukuba luzibandakanye ekuncedeni.
Wathi: "Sisenokuninzi ekusafuneka sifunde ngamalulwane ethu yaye ezininzi zeentlobo zethu zezilwanyana asizazi ukuba ziphila njani".
URonaldo uyazikhaba ngaw' omane izityholo zokudlwengula njengoko amagqwetha azimisele ukumangalela iphephancwadi laseJamani
UCristiano Ronaldo uye wabagxeka ngelithi "ziindaba zobuxoki" izityholo zokudlwengulwa kwakhe, esithi abantu "bafuna ukuzithengisa" ngokusebenzisa igama lakhe.
Amagqwetha akhe azimisele ukumangalela iphephancwadi laseJamani iDer Spiegel, elapapasha izityholo.
Umdlali weqela lasePortugal nelaseJuventus utyholwa ngokudlwengula ibhinqa laseMerika, uKathryn Mayorga, kwigumbi lasehotele eLas Vegas ngowama-2009.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba wamhlawula i-$375,000 ukuze athule ngale ngxaki, ngokutsho kwephephandaba iDer Spiegel ngoLwesihlanu.
Ethetha kwividiyo ye-Instagram Live kubalandeli bakhe abazizigidi ezili-142 kwiiyure ezimbalwa emva kokuba ezi zityholo zixelwe, uRonaldo, oneminyaka engama-33 ubudala, wazigxeka ezi ngxelo esithi "ziindaba zobuxoki".
"Hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi.
Oko bakuthethileyo namhlanje, ziindaba ezingezizo", utsho umnqobi weBallon d'Or izihlandlo ezihlanu phambi kwekhamera.
"Bafuna ukuzithethelela besebenzisa igama lam.
Yinto eqhelekileyo.
Bafuna ukuba ngabantu abadumileyo ukuze bakwazi ukuthetha igama lam, kodwa yinxalenye yomsebenzi wabo.
Ndingumntu owonwabileyo kwaye konke kulungile", lo mdlali wongezelela, encumile.
Amagqwetha kaRonaldo alungiselela ukumangalela iDer Spiegel ngenxa yezityholo, ezibize ngokuba "kukunikela ingxelo engavumelekanga ngamathandabuzo kwindawo yobumfihlo", ngokutsho kweReuters.
Igqwetha uChristian Schertz lithi lo mdlali uza kufuna intlawulo "ngomonakalo owenziwe kuye, umlinganiselo wawo ofana nobungakanani bomonakalo owenziwe, nto leyo ekusenokwenzeka ukuba yenye yezona zenzo zothusayo zokuphulwa kwamalungelo abantu kwiminyaka yakutshanje".
Kuthiwa esi siganeko senzeka ngoJuni 2009 kwindlu yehotele ekuthiwa yiPalms Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Emva kokudibana kwiqela lasebusuku, uRonaldo noMayorga kuthiwa babuyela kwigumbi lomdlali, apho kuthiwa wamdlwengula ngomlomo, ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu afakwe kwiNkundla yeSithili saseClark County eNevada.
UMayorga uthi uRonaldo wawa ngamadolo emva kwesiganeko esithi senzeke waza wamxelela ukuba "99%" wayeyindoda "elungileyo" elahlekiswe "ngomnye ekhulwini".
La maxwebhu athi uRonaldo waqinisekisa ukuba esi sibini sasisoloko silala, kodwa kwaba ngemvume yomntu ngamnye.
UMajorga uthi waya emapoliseni waza wathatha iifoto zezivubeko zakhe esibhedlele, kodwa kamva wavuma ukuba angenele isivumelwano ngaphandle kwenkundla kuba wayeziva "esoyika ukubuyiselwa" kwaye exhalabele "ukuthotywa esidlangalaleni".
Lo dade uneminyaka engama-34 ubudala uthi ngoku ufuna ukuyiguqula le nto ayenzileyo njengoko esaqhubeka ebuhlungu ngenxa yeso siganeko.
URonaldo wayesele eza kujoyina iReal Madrid esuka eManchester United ngexesha lokuhlaselwa, kwaye kweli hlobo uye kwiqela laseItali iJuve ngesivumelwano esixabisa i-100 yezigidi zeerandi.
I-Brexit: I-UK 'iya kuxolela ngonaphakade' ukulahlekelwa ngabenzi bemoto
UGreg Clark, uNobhala Wezoshishino uthi, i-UK "iya kuzisola ngonaphakade" ukuba iyaphulukana nesikhundla sayo njengenkokeli yehlabathi kwimveliso yeemoto emva kweBrexit.
Wongezelela ukuba "kuxhalabisa" ukuba iToyota UK ixelele iBBC ukuba ukuba iBritane ishiye i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano iya kumisa okwethutyana imveliso kumzi-mveliso wayo eBurnaston, kufuphi neDerby.
UMnu. Clark wathi: "Sifuna ukwenza isivumelwano".
Umvelisi weemoto waseJapan wathi impembelelo yokulibaziseka kwemida kwimeko ye-Brexit engenayo inokubiza imisebenzi.
Umzi-mveliso waseBurnaston - owenza iAuris neAvensis zakwaToyota - wavelisa iimoto eziphantse zibe li-150 000 kunyaka ophelileyo, apho i90% yazo yathunyelwa kwamanye amazwe e-European Union.
UMarvin Cooke, onguMlawuli weToyota eBurnaston wathi: "Imbono yam kukuba ukuba iBritani iyaphuma kwi-EU ekupheleni kukaMatshi, siya kubona imveliso iyeka kumzi-mveliso wethu".
Abanye abavelisi beemoto base-UK baye bavakalisa uloyiko malunga nokuphuma kwe-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano malunga nendlela urhwebo oluya kusebenza ngayo, kuquka iHonda, iBMW kunye neJaguar Land Rover.
Ngokomzekelo, i-BMW ithi iza kuvala umzi-mveliso wayo iMini eOxford kangangeenyanga emva kweBrexit.
Eyona nto ixhalabisa kakhulu ngabenzi bemoto kukuba banokuzichanaba njani xa kungekho nto ixoxwayo ngeBrexit.
Imveliso yeToyota isebenza "ngexesha elifanelekileyo", kunye neendawo ezifika rhoqo emva kwemizuzu engama-37 ezivela kubanikezeli bezithuthi e-UK nase-EU.
Ukuba i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngomhla wama-29 kwinyanga kaMatshi, kunokubakho ukuphazamiseka emdeni okuya kukhokelela ekulibaziseni nasekunqongophaleni kwezinto.
Le nkampani yathi, iToyota ayinakukwazi ukugcina izinto ezaneleyo zokutya usuku olunye kwisitya sayo esiseDerbyshire, yaye ngoko ke imveliso iya kumiswa.
UMnu Clark uthe uCheresa May's Chequers uceba ubudlelwane bexesha elizayo ne-EU "ngokuchanekileyo ukuze kuphetshwe ukuphepha ezo zinto kwi-border".
"Kufuneka senze isivumelwano. Sifuna ukwenza esona sivumelwano sihle esiya kuthi, njengoko ndisitsho, singaneli nje ukuvuyela impumelelo ekhoyo kodwa sifumane eli thuba", utshilo kwiBBC Radio 4's Today.
"Ubungqina obuvela kwiToyota kodwa nakwabanye abavelisi kukuba kufuneka sikwazi ukuqhubeka noko kuye kwaphumelela kakhulu kwiinkqubo zokubonelela".
UToyota akazange akwazi ukuchaza ukuba uza kuyeka ukuvelisa ixesha elingakanani, kodwa ke walumkisa ngelithi kwixesha elide, iindleko ezongezelelweyo ziza kunciphisa ukhuphiswano lwezityalo ze ekugqibeleni zilahlekise ngemisebenzi.
UPeter Tsouvallaris osebenze eBurnaston iminyaka engama-24 kwaye ungumhlanganisi weYunithi yomanyano kumzi-mveliso, uthe amalungu akhe aya exhalaba: "Ngokwamava am xa le misebenzi sele ihambile ayisekho.
Isithethi sikarhulumente sathi: "Siphakamise isicwangciso esicacileyo nesithembekileyo sobudlelwane bethu bexesha elizayo ne-EU".
Intlanganiso kaTrump noRosenstein inokuphinda ilibaziseke, itsho iNdlu ye-White House
Intlanganiso kaDonald Trump kunye noSekela Mongameli uRod Rosenstein "inokuhlehliswa ngeveki enye" njengoko kuqhubeka umlo malunga nomntu ogqityelweyo kwiNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh, iNdlu ye-White House ithe ngeCawa.
URosenstein ujonga umsebenzi womgqwetha okhethekileyo uRobert Mueller, ophanda ngokungenelela kwamaRashiya kunyulo, unxibelelwano phakathi kwabancedisi bakaTrump neRashiya kunye nokuthintelwa kobulungisa ngumongameli.
Ukuthi uTrump uza kumgxotha kusini na isekela-mtshutshisi-jikelele, yaye ngaloo ndlela abubeke esichengeni inkululeko kaMueller, kuye kwavuselela intlebendwane yaseWashington kangangeenyanga.
Ekuqaleni kwale nyanga, iNew York Times yanikela ingxelo yokuba uRosenstein wayexubusha ngokunxiba ucingo ukuze aqophe iingxoxo kunye noTrump kwakunye nokuba kunokwenzeka ukuba asuse umongameli ngokusebenzisa isilungiso sama-25.
URosenstein wayikhaba loo ngxelo.
Kodwa ngoMvulo odluleyo waya kwiNdlu ye-White House, phakathi kweengxelo zokuba wayeza kuyeka.
