Abathengi basemzini baza kuhlawuliswa intlawulo ephezulu xa bethenga izindlu eBritani - imali eyongezelelweyo iza kusetyenziswa ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya, uTheresa May uza kuvakalisa namhlanje.
Le ntshukumo iya kujongwa njengokuzama ukuphazamisa impumelelo yephulo likaJeremy Corbyn lokutsala abavoti abatsha ngezithembiso zokunikezela ngezindlu ezifikelelekayo nokujolisa kwabo bafumana umvuzo ophezulu.
Ukwanda kweentlawulo zezitampu kuya kuhlawulwa kubantu ngabanye nakwiinkampani ezingahlawuli rhafu e-UK, kunye nemali eyongezelelweyo yokunyusa umzamo kaRhulumente wokulwa nokulala.
Intlawulo eyongezelelweyo - eyongezelelweyo kwintlawulo yangoku, kuquka namazinga aphezulu aqaliswe kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo kwimizi yesibini kunye nokuthenga-ukuya-kwizindlu-kunokuba ngaphezu kwepesenti ezintathu.
Urhulumente ulindele ukuba le ntshukumo izise imali efikelela kwi-120 lezigidi zeepounds ngonyaka.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba i-13% yezakhiwo ezitsha zaseLondon zithengwa ngabantu abangengabo abahlali base-UK, nto leyo eyenza amaxabiso anyuke ize yenze kube nzima kubathengi abaqalayo ukuba bangene kwizindlu.
Iindawo ezininzi ezifumileyo zeli lizwe - ngokukodwa kwikomkhulu - ziye zaba "ziidolophu eziphithizelayo" ngenxa yenani elikhulu labathengi abavela kwamanye amazwe abachitha ixesha labo elininzi ngaphandle kweli lizwe.
Le nkqubo intsha iza emva kweeveki nje uBoris Johnson ebize ukuba kuncitshiswe intlawulo yezitampu ukuze kuncedwe abantu abaselula babe namakhaya abo okuqala.
Uthe amaqumrhu amakhulu okwakha agcina amaxabiso ezindlu ephezulu ngokuqokelela umhlaba kodwa angawusebenzisi, kwaye wabongoza uNkosikazi May ukuba ayeke ukufaka izindlu ezifikelelekayo ukuze alungise "intloni yezindlu" yaseBritane.
UMnu. Corbyn uye wabhengeza uthotho lweenguqulelo ezibangela umdla ezicetywayo zokwakhiwa kwezindlu, kuquka ukulawula irente nokupheliswa kokugxothwa kwabantu "ngaphandle kwesizathu".
Ufuna ukunika amabhunga amandla angakumbi okwakha amakhaya amatsha.
UNkosikazi May uthe: "Kulo nyaka uphelileyo ndathi ndiza kunikela ngobuntloko bam ekubuyiseleni iphupha laseBritane - lokuba ubomi bube bhetele kwisizukulwana ngasinye esitsha.
Yaye oko kuthetha ukulungisa imarike yethu yezindlu eyonakeleyo.
IBritani iya kusoloko ivulelekile kubantu abafuna ukuhlala, ukusebenza nokwakha ubomi apha.
Nangona kunjalo, akunakuba yinto elungileyo ukuba kube lula kubantu abangahlali e-UK, kunye neenkampani ezizinze kumazwe angaphandle, ukuthenga amakhaya njengabemi baseBritane abasebenza nzima.
Kubantu abaninzi iphupha lokuba nekhaya liye laba yinto nje ekude, yaye ukulala phandle kuyinto engekhoyo".
