Iindlela onokukhetha ukuxhasa ngazo imali yokunyamekela abantu abakwixesha elide zinokuquka ipolisi yeinshorensi yokunyamekela abantu abakwixesha elide, ipolisi yeinshorensi yobomi enexabiso elixutywe ngokwemali ukuze uncedise ukuhlawula ezi ndleko okanye ukuzithengela i-inshorensi ngobutyebi bakho - logama nje unemali.
Zilungiselele kakuhle izinto ezisemthethweni, uphephe iimfazwe zomthetho eziya kuqhubeka apho.
Yenza ummeli wempilo ukuze umisele umntu omthembileyo ukuba akunyamekele aze aqinisekise ukuba oogqirha bayavumelana neminqweno yakho xa ungakwazi ukunxibelelana.
