Indoda idutyulwe izihlandlo ezininzi ngesibhamu somoya eIlfracombe
Indoda ethile idutyulwe izihlandlo eziliqela ngenqwelo-mafutha njengoko yayihamba ibuyela ekhaya emva kokuphuma phandle.
Ixhoba, elineminyaka engaphezu kwama-40, lalikummandla waseOxford Grove wase-Ilfracombe, eDevon, xa ladutyulwa esifubeni, esiswini nasesandleni.
Amagosa ayichaza le nto yenzeka malunga ne-02:30 BST, "njengesenzo esiqhutywa ngengozi".
Ixhoba alizange liyibone loo mntu uhlaselayo.
