Iinyikima Neetsunami EIndonesia
Abantu abangama-384 baye babulawa yinyikima enkulu eyahlasela isixeko sasePalu eIndonesia ngoLwesihlanu, yaye inani labantu abafayo kulindeleke ukuba lenyuke, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni.
Ngenxa yokuba unxibelelwano luyekile, amagosa ancedayo akakwazanga ukufumana naluphi na ulwazi kwiDonggala, ummandla ongasentla kwePalu okufuphi kwindawo eyafikelwa yinyikima enkulu.
EPalu, abantu abangaphezu kwe - 16 000 bakhutshwa emva kwentlekele.
Nazi ezinye iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo ngePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseSulawesi:
IPalu likomkhulu lephondo elikuMbindi Sulawesi, elikuyo ekupheleni kwe bay emxinwa kunxweme olusentshona kwisiqithi Sulawesi, elinabemi abaqikelelwa kuma 379,800 ngo 2017.
Esi sixeko sasibhiyozela isikhumbuzo seminyaka engama-40 sikho xa kwafika inyikima netsunami.
I-Donggala ngummandla ongasentla-ntshona wesiqithi iSulawesi ononxweme oluphantse lube ziikhilomitha ezingama - 300 (iikhilomitha ezingama - 180).
I-regency, ummandla olawulayo ongaphantsi kwephondo, unabemi abaqikelelwa kuma-299,200 ngo-2017.
Uqoqosho lwephondo iCentral Sulawesi, ingakumbi kummandla ongaselunxwemeni waseDonggala, luxhomekeke ekulobeni nasekulimeni.
Imigodi ye-nickel nayo ibalulekile kweli phondo, kodwa ikakhulu igxile eMorowali, kunxweme oluphambene neSulawesi.
Ngokutsho kwe-Arhente Yokunciphisa Iintlekele YaseIndonesia, iPalu neDonggala ziye zafikelwa ziitsunami izihlandlo eziliqela kule minyaka ili-100 idluleyo.
Ngowe-1938, itsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 yaza yatshabalalisa amakhulu amakhaya eDonggala.
Ngowe-1996, i-tsunami yahlasela kwintshona yeDonggala, yaza yabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ihlala kwiPacific Ring of Fire yaye ihlala ibethwa ziinyikima.
Nantsi eminye yemihlaselo emikhulu yenyikima neitsunami eye yenzeka kwiminyaka yakutshanje:
Ngowama-2004: Inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona lwephondo laseIndonesia iAce kumantla eSumatra ngoDisemba 26 yabangela itsunami eyahlasela amazwe ali-14, yabulala abantu abangama-226,000 kunxweme loLwandlekazi lwaseIndiya, abangaphezu kwesiqingatha kubo eAceh.
Ngowama - 2005: Iintlitha zenyikima ezinkulu zantlitha unxweme olusentshona lweSumatra ekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kukaAprili.
Amakhulu afa kwisiQithi saseNias, kunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngowama-2006: Ukhukuliseko olungama - 6,8 lwagqabhuka kumazantsi eJava, esona siqithi sineyona ndawo inabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, lwabangela itsunami eyahlasela unxweme olusemazantsi, yaza yabulala abantu abaphantse babe ngama - 700.
Ngowama-2009: Ilizwe linyikima ngamandla ayi-7.6 kufutshane nesixeko iPadang, elikomkhulu lephondo leNtshona yeSumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngowama - 2010: Inyikima enkulu ebinga 7.5 kwiRichter yahlasela esinye seziqithi iMentawai, kufutshane neSumatra, yabangela itsunami enamandla kangangeemitha ezili - 10 eyabulala iidolophana ezininzi yaza yabulala abantu abamalunga nama - 300.
Ngo-2016: Inyikima encinane yabetha iPidie Jaya eAceh, ibangela umonakalo kunye noxinzelelo njengoko abantu bekhunjuzwa ngomonakalo wenyikima eyingozi ka-2004 kunye netsunami.
Akukhange kubekho tsunami kwesi sihlandlo, kodwa abantu abangaphezu kwe-100 babulawa zizakhiwo eziwileyo.
Ngowe-2018: Iintlekele ezinkulu zatshabalalisa isiqithi saseIndonesia esiyiLombok, kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwama-500, uninzi lwabo lwalusemantla eso siqithi.
Le nyikima yatshabalalisa izakhiwo ezininzi yaza yashiya abakhenkethi abaninzi bevaleleke kwiindawo ezingaphandle kwezindlu zabo.
Unyana Omdala KaSarah Palin Uyabanjwa Ngokumangalelwa Ngokwenza Ugonyamelo Ekhaya
UTrek Palin, unyana omdala owayesakuba ngumphathi waseAlaska nowayesakuba ngumgqatswa kwilinge lakhe lokuba ngumsekela-mongameli uSarah Palin, uye wabanjwa ngenxa yokutyholwa ngokudlwengula.
UPalin, oneminyaka engama-29 ubudala, waseWasilla, eAlaska, wabanjwa ngenxa yokurhanelwa ngogonyamelo lwasekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yogonyamelo lwasekhaya nokumelana nokubanjwa, ngokwengxelo ekhutshwe ngoMgqibelo ngamaGosa kaRhulumente eAlaska.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo yamapolisa, xa umntu awayemazi wazama ukufowunela amapolisa ukuze axele ngolwaphulo-mthetho olucelwayo, wayithatha ifowuni yakhe.
I-KTUU ithi uPalin ugcinwa kwiMat-Su Pre-trial Facility yaye ugcinwe kwi-$500 bond engaqinisekiswanga.
I-TV yachaza ukuba wavela enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, apho wavakalisa ukuba "akanatyala, ngokuqinisekileyo" xa ebuzwa ukuba uyavuma na.
UPalin ujongene namatyala amathathu oDidi A, nto leyo ethetha ukuba unokubanjwa kangangonyaka uze uhlawuliswe i-$250,000.
Kwakhona utyholwa ngokwaphula umthetho okuDidi B, okuhlwayelwa ngomhla ejele nangentlawulo engange-$2,000 (R2.000).
Asikokokuqala ukuba uPalin abekwe ityala lokwaphulwa komthetho.
NgoDisemba 2017, watyholwa ngokuhlasela uyise, uTodd Palin.
Unina, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuze axele ngento ekuthiwa kukuhlaselwa.
Ngoku eli tyala liseNkundleni Yamajoni AseMkhosini eAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016 wabekwa ityala lokuhlasela ekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yolwaphulo-mthetho lwasekhaya, kunye nokuba nesixhobo ngelixa wayenxilile ngokunxulumene nesiganeko.
Intombazana awayethandana nayo yathi wayibetha ngempama ebusweni.
USarah Palin wagxekwa ngamaqela omagqala omkhosi ngo-2016 emva kokudibanisa ukuziphatha konyana wakhe okunobundlobongela kwi-PTSD evela kwinkonzo yakhe e-Iraq.
Iintshukumo ze-Indonesia: amakhulu abulawa
