Abacuphi baseburhulumenteni bafuna isigwebo esinqabileyo sokubulawa komntu otyholwa ngokuhlasela iNew York
Abatshutshisi baseNew York bafuna isigwebo sentambo kuSayfullo Saipov, umrhanelwa wohlaselo lobugorha lwaseNew York olwabulala abantu abasibhozo - isigwebo esinqabileyo esingazange senziwe kweli lizwe ngenxa yolwaphulo-mthetho olwenziwa ngurhulumente ukususela ngowe-1953.
USaipov, oneminyaka engama-30 ubudala, kuthiwa wasebenzisa ilori eqeshwe yiHome Depot ukuze ahlasele indlela yebhayisekile ecaleni kweWest Side Highway eMzantsi Manhattan, egrumba abantu abahamba ngeenyawo nabahamba ngeebhayisekile endleleni yakhe ngo-Oktobha.
Ukuze kugwetywe isigwebo sentambo, abamangali kuza kufuneka bangqine ukuba uSayipov "ngamabomu" wabulala amaxhoba asibhozo waza "ngamabomu" wenza umonakalo omkhulu emzimbeni, ngokutsho kwesaziso senjongo yokufuna isigwebo sentambo, esifakwe kwiSithili saseMzantsi saseNew York.
La matyala mabini anokubangela ukuba ugwetywe ukufa, ngokutsho kwedokhumenti yasenkundleni.
Kwiiveki emva kolu hlaselo, ijaji enkulu yasekuhlaleni yamangalela uSaipov ngezibakala ezingama-22 eziquka izityholo ezisibhozo zokubulala ngenjongo yokuncedisa ekuqhatyeni, ngokuqhelekileyo ezisetyenziswa ngabatshutshisi baseburhulumenteni kumatyala olwaphulo-mthetho olulungelelanisiweyo, netyala lobundlobongela nokutshatyalaliswa kwezithuthi.
Abatshutshisi bathi, esi siganeko sasifuna "ukucwangciswa kwangaphambili", besithi indlela awawenza ngayo uSaipov "yayisenyanyeka, inkohlakalo yaye yayiphosakele".
Isaziso senjongo sithi: "USayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wenzakalisa, wenzakalisa, waza wabangela ilahleko kwiintsapho nakubahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicholas Cleves, uAnn-Laure Decadt, uDarren Drake, uAriel Erlij, uHernan Ferruchi, uHernan Diego Mendoza noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco".
Amahlanu kula maxhoba ayeziindwendwe zaseArgentina.
Sele kudlule iminyaka elishumi ukususela xa isithili esisezantsi saseNew York sagweba ityala elisingise kwisigwebo sokufa.
Ummangalelwa, uKhalid Barnes, wafunyaniswa enetyala lokubulala abathengisi beziyobisi ababini kodwa ekugqibeleni wagwetywa ubomi bakhe bonke entolongweni ngoSeptemba 2009.
Ixesha lokugqibela isigwebo sentambo senziwa kwicala laseNew York ngo-1953 kuJulius no-Ethel Rosenberg, isibini esitshatileyo esenziwa emva kokuba bagwetyelwe ukuceba ukwenza ubuhloli kwiSoviet Union ngexesha leMfazwe Yomlomo kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo.
Bobabini aba baRosenberg babulawa ngesitulo sombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
Ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu enkundla, uSaipov, ongummi waseUzbekistan, akazange abonakalise mvakalelo yokuzisola kwiintsuku neenyanga ezalandela emva kolu hlaselo.
Wathi abaphandi ukuba wayeziva elungile ngoko wayekwenzile, amapolisa athi.
Ngokutsho kwesityholo, uSayipov waxelela abasemagunyeni ukuba waphefumlelwa ukuba alwe emva kokuba ebukele iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe.
Kwakhona wacela ukuba kubekwe iflegi ye-ISIS kwigumbi lakhe esibhedlele, ngokutsho kwamapolisa.
Uye wavuma ukuba akanatyala kwizityholo ezingama-22.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabameli bakaSaipov, wathi "ngokucacileyo" badanile sisigqibo setyala.
"Sicinga ukuba isigqibo sokugweba ngokufa kunokuvuma ukuba unetyala lokuvalelwa ubomi bonke entolongweni kungekho ndlela yokukhululwa siya kulolula nje kuphela usizi lwezi ziganeko kubo bonke ababandakanyekileyo", utshilo uPatton.
Iqela elikhusela uSaipov lalisele licele abatshutshisi ukuba bangafuni isigwebo sentambo.
