Iinyikima ezinamandla zisaqhubeka zityhwatyhwa le ndawo yaye uninzi lwazo lubhaxwe ziingqushu kwisixeko sasePalu.
Kodwa nangona oontanga bakhe babebaleka ukuze baphephe, uAnthonius Gunawan Agung oneminyaka engama-21 ubudala akazange avume ukushiya isikhundla sakhe kwisakhiwo esilawulayo esikwiMutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport Palu.
Wahlala apho ukuze aqiniseke ukuba iBatik Air Flight 6321, eyayikwindlela yokunduluka ngelo xesha, ikwazile ukusuka ngokukhuselekileyo.
Emva koko watsiba kwisakhiwo esilawula izithuthi xa wayecinga ukuba siza kuwa.
Kamva wafa esibhedlele.
Isithethi seAir Navigation Indonesia, uYohannes Sirait, wathi esi sigqibo sinokuba sisindise ubomi bamakhulu abantu, ingxelo yeABC News yaseOstreliya.
Salungiselela inqwelo - moya enophephela ngeenqwelo - moya ukusuka eBalikpapan eKalimantan ukuze simse kwisibhedlele esikhulu esikwesinye isixeko.
Ngelishwa, silahlekelwe nguye ngale ntsasa phambi kokuba i-helicopter ifike ePalu.
Wongezelela ngelithi: "Iintliziyo zethu ziyaphuka xa sisiva oku".
Okwangoku, abasemagunyeni boyika ukuba inani labantu abaswelekileyo lisenokufikelela kumawaka, kuba i-arhente yokunciphisa intlekele ithi ukufikelela kwiidolophu zaseDonggala, Sigi naseBoutong kulinganiselwe.
"Kukholelwa ukuba inani labantu lisenokwanda kuba imizimba emininzi isaphantsi kweengcwaba kanti ininzi ayikakwazi ukufunyanwa", utsho uSutopo Purwo Nugroho osisithethi sale nkampani.
Amaza anobude obufikelela kwiimitha ezintandathu atshabalalise iPalu apho kuza kubekwa umngcwabo omkhulu ngeCawa.
Iinqwelomoya zemfazwe nezorhwebo zizisa uncedo nezinto zokunceda.
URisa Kusuma, umama oneminyaka engama-35 ubudala, waxelela iSky News oku: "Mzuzu ngamnye kuza inqwelo-moto yezigulana izise izidumbu.
Amanzi acocekileyo anqabile.
Iivenkile ezincinane ziphangwa kuyo yonke indawo".
UJan Gelfand, intloko ye-International Red Cross e-Indonesia, uxelele i-CNN: "ISixeko sase-Indonesia esiBomvu sikhawuleza ukunceda abasindileyo kodwa asazi ukuba baza kufumana ntoni apho.
