Iinani labathinjwa baseMntla Korea 'bayehla' phantsi kukaKim
Inani labantu baseMntla Korea abaye bayishiya iKorea baya eMzantsi Korea liye lehla ukususela oko uKim Jong-un weza elawula kwiminyaka esixhenxe edlulileyo, utsho umenzi-mthetho waseMzantsi Korea.
UPark Byeong-seug, ocaphula inkcazelo evela kwiSebe Elijongene Nokudibanisa Abantu, uthi kunyaka ophelileyo kuye kwabakho abantu abayi-1 127 abaye bayeka ukuba ngamaKristu - xa kuthelekiswa nabayi-2 706 ngowama-2011.
UMnu Park uthe ukuqiniswa kokulawulwa kwemida phakathi kweNorth Korea neChina kunye namaxabiso aphezulu abizwa ngabarhwebi ngabantu ngawona manqanaba abalulekileyo.
UPyongyang akazange athethe nto.
Uninzi lwabantu abaphambukayo abavela eMntla ekugqibeleni banikwa ubumi baseMzantsi Korea.
ISeoul ithi abantu baseMntla Korea abangaphezu kwama-30,000 baye banqumla ngokungekho mthethweni kumda ukususela ekupheleni kweMfazwe yaseKorea ngowe-1953.
Uninzi lwazo luthi luhambe ngeChina, eyona inemida emide neNorth Korea yaye kulula ukuyinqumla kunomda okhuselweyo phakathi kweKorea neChina.
IChina ibona ababaleki njengabantu abafudukayo ngokungekho mthethweni kunokuba babe ziimbacu ibe ngokufuthi ibabuyisela ngenkani kwilizwe labo.
Ulwalamano phakathi kweMntla noMzantsi - ezingekho emfazweni - luye lwaphucuka ngokuphawulekayo kwezi nyanga zidluleyo.
Ekuqaleni kwale nyanga, iinkokeli zamazwe amabini zidibene ePyongyang ngeengxoxo ezazigxile kwiingxoxo eziyekileyo zokupheliswa kwezikhali zenyukliya.
Oku kwenzeka emva kwentlanganiso eyimbali kaJuni phakathi koMongameli wase-US uDonald Trump noKim Jong-un eSingapore, xa bavumelana ngokubanzi ukuba basebenze kwiphondo laseKorea elingenazixhobo zenyukliya.
Kodwa ngoMgqibelo, uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uRi Yong-ho utyhole i-US ngezohlwayo ngenxa yokungabikho kwenkqubela ukususela ngoko.
