Imfazwe yorhwebo yase-US-China inokuba yinto entle njani kwi-Beijing
Iingcali zithi, ukuqala kweemfazwe zorhwebo phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina kwakusitsho iindlebe, yaye nangona le mfazwe isekude ukuba iphele, ukwahlukana phakathi kwala mazwe kusenokuba luncedo eBeijing ekuhambeni kwexesha.
UMongameli waseUnited States uDonald Trump, walumkisa ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka ngokuthengisa izinto eziphambili zaseTshayina eziquka iiphaneli zelanga, isinyithi nealuminiyam.
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo yenzeke kule veki, kukuthotyelwa kweerhafu entsha kwiimpahla ezixabisa i-$200 billion (i-£150 billion), nto leyo ethetha ukuba isiqingatha sayo yonke impahla evela eChina isiya e-US.
I-Beijing iye yaluziphindezela olo hlobo, kutshanje ibeka iirhafu eziphakathi kwee-5% ne-10% kwiimveliso zaseMerika ezixabisa i-$60 yezigidigidi.
IChina iye yazibophelela ukuba iza kufanelana ne-United States, yaye akubonakali ngathi eli lizwe likhulu ehlabathini liya kuba nexesha elide lifuna ukuva oko.
Ukuvumela iWashington ukuba ibuye umva kuthetha ukuzinikezela kwiimfuno, kodwa ukuzithoba esidlangalaleni kwi-US kuya kuba lihlazo kakhulu ku-Xi Jinping, umongameli wase-China.
Sekunjalo, iingcali zithi ukuba iBeijing inokuzidlala kakuhle, uxinzelelo lweemfazwe zorhwebo zaseMerika lunokuyixhasa iChina kwixesha elide ngokunciphisa ukuxhomekeka kweziqoqosho zimbini.
UAbigail Grace, ophanda ngeAsia kwiCenter for New American Security, uthi: "Inyaniso yokuba isigqibo esiphuthumayo kwezopolitiko eWashington okanye eBeijing sinokudala iimeko eziya kwenza ukuba ezoqoqosho ziguquke kweli lizwe okanye kwelinye, iyingozi ngakumbi kunokuba abanye abantu bebesoloko besitsho".
ISyria 'ikulungele' ukubuyisela iimbacu, utsho uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle
ISiriya ithi ilungele ukubuyela ngokuthanda kwayo kwiimbacu kwaye icela uncedo ukuze iphinde yakhe eli lizwe litshabalaliswe yimfazwe yeminyaka esixhenxe.
Ethetha kwiNdibano yoWiso-mthetho yeZizwe eziManyeneyo, umphathiswa wezangaphandle uWalid al-Moualem wathi iimeko kweli lizwe ziyaphucuka.
"Namhlanje imeko emhlabeni izinzile kwaye ikhuselekile ngenxa yenkqubela eyenziweyo ekulweni nobugrogrisi", utshilo.
Urhulumente uyaqhubeka nokuhlaziya iindawo ezonakaliswe ngabanqolobi ukuze abuyisele imeko eqhelekileyo.
Ngoku zonke iimeko zikho ukuze ababaleki babuyele ngokuzithandela kumazwe abo ababewashiya ngenxa yobunqolobi namalungiselelo ezoqoqosho awayesenziwa ngabom awayejoliswe kubomi babo bemihla ngemihla nakwimeko yabo yokuphila.
IUN iqikelela ukuba bangaphezu kwezigidi ezi-5,5 abantu baseSiriya abaye basaba kwelo lizwe ukususela ekuqaleni kwemfazwe ngowama-2011.
Ezinye izigidi ezithandathu zabantu ezisahlala kweli lizwe zifuna uncedo.
U-Al-Moualem uthe urhulumente waseSiriya uza kuluvuyela uncedo ekwakheni ilizwe elidlakaziweyo.
Kodwa wagxininisa ngelithi ibingayi kwamkela uncedo olunemiqathango okanye uncedo oluvela kumazwe axhasa imvukelo.
