Inkwenkwezi yaseMelika uPhil Mickelson, owayenengxaki enkulu kulo mdlalo, wafaka i-tee-shot yakhe emanzini kumgodi we-16 we-par-3, wafumana umdlalo wakhe kuFrancesco Molinari.
Umgadi wegalufa waseItali uMolinari waqaqamba kuwo onke amanqanaba akhe, waba ngomnye wabadlali abane abathi baye kwi-5-0-0 ukususela kwimo yexesha langoku le tumente eyaqala ngowe-1979.
