Uhlaziyo oluvela kwiRed Tide: Ukuxinana kwehla ePinellas, Manatee naseSarasota
Ingxelo yakutshanje evela kwiFlorida Fish and Wildlife Commission ibonisa ukuba abantu abaninzi baye banciphisa i-Red Tide kwiindawo ezithile zaseTampa Bay.
Ngokutsho kwe-FWC, iimeko ze-patchier bloom ziyabikwa kwimimandla ye-Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte kunye ne-Collier counties-ebonisa ukunciphisa ukuxinana.
I-Red Tide isasazeka malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-130 ukusuka kumantla wePinellas ukuya kumzantsi weLee counties.
Iindawo ezinamabala zinokufunyanwa malunga neekhilomitha ezili-10 kude nonxweme lweHillsborough County, kodwa kwiindawo ezimbalwa xa kuthelekiswa neveki ephelileyo.
I-Red Tide iye yabonwa nakwiphondo lasePasco.
Iindawo ezinomlinganiselo ophakathi okanye eziphesheya kwelizwe lasePinellas ziye zachazwa kwiveki edlulileyo, iindawo ezinomlinganiselo ophantsi ukuya phezulu kwilizwe laseHillsborough, indawo ephantsi ukuya phezulu kwilizwe laseManatee, indawo ephantsi ukuya phezulu kwilizwe laseSarasota, indawo ephantsi ukuya kumlinganiselo ophakathi kwilizwe laseCharlotte, indawo ephantsi ukuya phezulu kwilizwe laseLee, kunye neendawo eziphantsi kwilizwe laseCollier.
Ukudumba komoya kuqhubeka kunikwa ingxelo kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, nelaseCollier.
Akukho ngxelo zothuko lokuphefumla eziye zafunyanwa eMntla-Ntshona Florida kule veki iphelileyo.
